quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,S leûfuf d tirni
  37,2,"S tid i t inehôen, nehôent"
  37,3,S tid iqqaôen asmekti
  37,4,"Öebbi nnwen, s tidep, ard Yiwen"
  37,5,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, Mass n yigmav"
  37,6,"Ih, Ncebbeê igenni aqôib mavi, s ccbaêa n yitran"
  37,7,i uêareb si yal cciîan amnafeq
  37,8,"ur ssemêasen i le$wat aâlayen nezzeh; ad pwaôeomen, si yal tama"
  37,9,ad pwanfun; fellasen aâaqeb idumen
  37,10,"Ma illa win iccleqfen ayen iccelqef, a t id ivfeô usafu ifellun"
  37,11,"Steqsi ten: day nitni, axlaq nnsen, iwâaô sennig win n wiyav, i Nexleq? Ni$ Nexleq iten s talaxt ibbelîuvêen"
  37,12,"Xaîi, twehmev, la ttihin"
  37,13,"Ma pwafekkôen d, ur d smektayen"
  37,14,"Ma walan assekni, ad mmaâlken"
  37,15,"Nnan: \"wagi, ih, iban kan d ssêur"
  37,16,"Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, d i$san, day a d nu$al"
  37,17,akked lejdud nne$ imezwura
  37,18,"Ini: \"ih, u a ppilim d imedlulen"
  37,19,"Yiwet n ti$ôi kan, d$a nitni pmuqulen"
  37,20,"Nnan: \"a ssexv nne$, wagi d ass uqeîîi"
  37,21,"Wagi d ass uêuddu, i$ef tellam d inekkaôen"
  37,22,"Ssemlilet ed wid idensen, tilawin nnsen, akked wayen âabden"
  37,23,war ÔÖebbi. Nehôet pen s abrid n wu$ud. ¨¨
  37,24,"Eîîfet pen, ih, nitni fellasen asteqsi. Ê"
  37,25,Ay$eô ur teppemsellakem
  37,26,"Xaîi! Assa, nitni ad fken mayna"
  37,27,"Ad zzin kra degsen, ar wiyav, pmesteqsayen"
  37,28,"Ad inin: \"ni$ kunwi teppasem d $uône$, s tgallit"
  37,29,"A d inin: \"xaîi, ur tellim d lmumnin"
  37,30,"Ur nesâi kra udabu, fellawen. Xaîi, tellam d agdud ijuôen"
  37,31,"Iûaô fella$ wawal n Mass nne$, aql a$, ih, la nessisin"
  37,32,"Nes$eôq ikwen; nella, nekwni, d i$eôôaqen"
  37,33,"Ih, assen, nitni, deg uâaqeb ad dduklen"
  37,34,"Akka, s tidep, ay Nxeddem i ibe$wviyen"
  37,35,"Ih, nitni, mara asen inin: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi\", ssem$waôen iman nnsen"
  37,36,"Qqaôen: \"day a neoo iôebbiten nne$, ilmend umedyaz aôehbani"
  37,37,"Xaîi, iusa d s tidep, itebbet ed imazanen"
  37,38,"Kunwi, war ccekk, a pjeôôben aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  37,39,"A ppeppuqeîîim kan, af wayen txeddmem"
  37,40,kkes ed imdanen n Öebbi izedganen
  37,41,"I widak, l$it ipwassnen"
  37,42,lfakya; u nitni ad ppuâuzzen
  37,43,di leonanat isaâdiyen
  37,44,Mqabalen $ef imîeôêen
  37,45,Ad asen tezzin s lkas n waman ipfeggiven
  37,46,"D imellalen, d iéidanen i wid itessen"
  37,47,"Ur qeôôêen, ur helken"
  37,48,"£uôsen, sut wallen ibran"
  37,49,"nitenti, am tmelli iffren"
  37,50,"Ad zzin, kra $eô kra, pmesteqsayen"
  37,51,"Yiwen id ihedôen, segsen, inna d: \"illa $uôi umeddakwel"
  37,52,"iyi d iqqaôen: \"ma, d ûûeê, keçç, seg wid issawalen tidep"
  37,53,"Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, akked i$san, day mazal fella$ îîlaba"
  37,54,"Inna: \"kunwi ma la tepmuqulem"
  37,55,"Imuqel, iwala t di pnaûfa n wu$ud"
  37,56,"Inna d: \"s Öebbi, ar qôib iyi tessôuêev"
  37,57,"Lemmer maççi d tacvaî n Mass iw, yili aql i seg wid id irsen"
  37,58,Day ur nepmeppat ara
  37,59,"Tameppant nne$ kan tamezwarut, nekwni ur neppuâaqab"
  37,60,"Ayagi, s tidep, d arraz ameqwôaêan"
  37,61,"I wayen icban aya, aânut a wid iâannun"
  37,62,"D wagi ay d axxam igerzen, ne$ d ttejôa n Zaqqum"
  37,63,"Nerra p, ih, d ahewwel i imednas"
  37,64,"Neppat, ih, d ttejôa id iff$en si pnaûfa n tmes"
  37,65,"Ppemôa s, amzun d iqweôôa n ccwaîen"
  37,66,"Nitni, war ccekk, ad ççen segs, ad ççaôen, segs, iâabbav"
  37,67,"Sinna, deffir es ad xelven aman ippayzagen"
  37,68,"Sinna, war ccekk, ad u$alen ar wu$ud"
  37,69,"Ih, ufan d ibabaten nnsen d im$eôôqen"
  37,70,"D$a nitni, di lateô nnsen, ddehmen"
  37,71,"Ni$ nnetlafen, uqbel nnsen, tegwti seg imezwura"
  37,72,Irna Nuzen asen ed ineddaôen
  37,73,Muqel amek tevôa d wid ipwanedôen
  37,74,kkes ed imdanen n Öebbi izedganen
  37,75,Ni$ Nuê inuj ed $uône£. Amaqwa n Wid ipjawaben
  37,76,"Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, si lefqaâ tabarart"
  37,77,"Nerra arraw is, d wid ara d iqqimen"
  37,78,Neooa d fellas i ineggura
  37,79,"talwit i Nuê, deg imavalen"
  37,80,"Ih, akka ay Nepkafi izedganen"
  37,81,"Neppa, ih, seg imdanen nne£ i iumnen"
  37,82,"Sinna, Ne$ôeq wiyav"
  37,83,"U si tnudda s, war ccekk: Ibôahim"
  37,84,"Mi d iusa, ar Mass is, s wul iûfan"
  37,85,"mi inna i baba s, akked ugdud is: \"d acu tâabdem"
  37,86,"D iôebbiten n tkerkas, war Öebbi, ay teb$am"
  37,87,Acu tepmeyyizem di Mass imavalen
  37,88,Iger tiî ar itran
  37,89,"inna: \"aql i ulwa"
  37,90,"Ooan t, wexxôen"
  37,91,"Izzi ar iôebbiten nnsen, inna: \"day ur teppeppem ara"
  37,92,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur d tneîqem ara"
  37,93,"Idhem fellasen, iwwet s uyeffus"
  37,94,"U$alen d $uôes, zeêêfen"
  37,95,"Inna: \"day a ppâabdem ayen tmeslem"
  37,96,"Öebbi Ixelq ikwen, akked wayen txeddmem"
  37,97,"Nnan: \"bnut as tazeqqa, terrem t ar wu$ud"
  37,98,B$an ad as p andin; Nekwni Nesseméi iten mavi
  37,99,"Inna: \"nek, ad ôuêe$ ar Mass iw, ad iyi Iawi d ubrid"
  37,100,"A Mass iw, £it iyi d, s iâaôviyen"
  37,101,Nbecceô it s tlalit n uqcic iêelmen
  37,102,"Mi ibda iteddu yides, inna: \"a mmi! Nek wala$, di targit, a k zlu$. Muqel d acu twalav\"? Inna: \"a baba! Exdem ayen ik ippumôen; ad iyi tafev, ma Irad Öebbi, seg iûebôiyen"
  37,103,"D$a, mi unzen, u iééel it $ef uniyr"
  37,104,"Nessawel as: \"a Ibôahim"
  37,105,"Tumnev s targit. Akka, ih, ay Nepkafi lâuûam"
  37,106,"Wagi, s tidep, d ajeôôeb n ûûeê"
  37,107,"Nefda t id, s tmezliwt tabarart"
  37,108,Neooa d fellas i ineggura
  37,109,tifrat i Ibôahim
  37,110,Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen
  37,111,"Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ iumnen"
  37,112,"Nbecceô it s Isêaq, d nnbi, seg iâaôviyen"
  37,113,"Nburek iten, neppa d Isêaq. Si tarwa nnsen, iban win iddan d ubrid, iban win idensen iman is"
  37,114,Ni$ N$at Musa akked Haôun
  37,115,"Nsellek iten, nitni akked ugdud nnsen, si lefqaâ tabarart"
  37,116,"Nefka yasen afus, d$a d nitni ay d imerbaê"
  37,117,Nefka yasen Tazmamt ipbegginen
  37,118,Nebbwi ten d ubrid uwqim
  37,119,"Neooa d fellasen, i ineggura"
  37,120,"talwit i Musa, akked Haôun"
  37,121,"Akka, ih, ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen"
  37,122,"Nitni, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ iumnen"
  37,123,"Ih, Ilyas ar seg imazanen"
  37,124,"Mi inna i ugdud is: \"day ur tepêezziben ara"
  37,125,"Day la tepnujum $eô Baâla, a ppeooem Üûam ixellaqen"
  37,126,"Öebbi, Mass nnwen, Mass n lejdud nnwen imezwura"
  37,127,"Skaddben t. S tidep, nitni a d rsen"
  37,128,"kkes ed imdanen n Öebbi, izedganen"
  37,129,"Neooa d fellas, i ineggura"
  37,130,talwit i Ilyas
  37,131,"Akka, ih, ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen"
  37,132,"Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ iumnen"
  37,133,"Ih, Luî seg imazanen"
  37,134,"Mi t Nsellek, akked twacult is, s lekmal is"
  37,135,"siwa tam$aôt, seg wid igwran"
  37,136,"Sinna, Nemêa wiyav"
  37,137,"Aql akwen la tleêêum fellasen, deg uzal"
  37,138,deg yiv. Day ur tepmeyyizem ara
  37,139,"Ih, Yunes ar seg imazanen"
  37,140,Mi irwel ar sfina iççuôen
  37,141,"Ijbed taseqqaôt, iûbeê ed seg wid ipwaveggôen"
  37,142,"Isseblaâ it uslem, u neppa degs tiyta"
  37,143,"Lemmer ur illi, neppa, seg wid isbuccuâen"
  37,144,"ad iqqim deg uâabbuv is, ar ass n tu$alin nnsen"
  37,145,"Nveggeô it id, s aqeôqaô, d amuvin"
  37,146,"Nessenker ed $uôes, ttejôa n texsayt"
  37,147,"Nuzen it ar twinas igima, uger"
  37,148,Umnen. Neooa ten zzhan kan tallit
  37,149,"Steqsi ten maday, i Mass ik, tullas; i nitni, arrac"
  37,150,"Ne$ Nexleq lmalayek d nnta, nitni d inagan"
  37,151,"Day, s tkerkas nnsen, ihi, a d inin"
  37,152,"Iurew ed Öebbi\"? Nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben"
  37,153,Ismenyaf tullas i warrac
  37,154,Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepêuddum
  37,155,Day ur d tesmektayem ara
  37,156,Ne$ tesâam adabu n ûûeê
  37,157,"Aset ed s tezmamt nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep"
  37,158,Gren d nnesba garaS d leonun. Irna leonun éôan ara d rsen
  37,159,"Gedha s Öebbi, mgal ayen qqaôen"
  37,160,Kkes ed imdanen n Öebbi izedganen
  37,161,"Ihi, kunwi, akked wayen tâabdem"
  37,162,"ur d tesskarem ahewwel, mgal iS"
  37,163,siwa win ara iô$en di tmes
  37,164,"Ur illi yiwen, degne$, ur nesâi amekkan ipwassnen"
  37,165,"Ih, nekwni d leûfuf"
  37,166,"Ih, nekwni d wid i isbuccuâen"
  37,167,Llan la qqaôen
  37,168,lemmer day $uône$ asmekti seg imezwura
  37,169,"a nili, war ccekk, d imdanen iâaôviyen n Öebbi"
  37,170,Nekôen T. Deqqal ad éôen
  37,171,"Ih, izwar ed wawal nne£, i imdanen nne£ imazanen"
  37,172,"Ih, d nitni ara ipwasellken"
  37,173,"S tidep, d iâsekôiwen nne£, ara irebêen"
  37,174,"Ihi, îîixeô asen kra n tallit"
  37,175,"Ssiked iten, deqqal ad walin"
  37,176,Day êaren af uâaqeb nne£
  37,177,"Ma irs ed ar umekkan nnsen, ay dir ip tûebêit n wid ippunedôen"
  37,178,Ïîixeô asen kra n tallit
  37,179,"Ssiked, deqqal ad walin"
  37,180,"Gedha s Mass ik, Mass n tezmert, mgal ayen qqaôen"
  37,181,Tifrat $ef imazanen
  37,182,"Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  38,1,Ü. S Leqwôan id ismektayen
  38,2,"Xaîi, wid ijehlen, atnan di tem$weô d ticuîna"
  38,3,"Acêal isuta ay Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen! Ssawlen d. Ur mazal akud i leslak"
  38,4,"Wehmen, iusa ten id uneddaô segsen. Nnan ijehliyen: \"wagi d aseêêar, d akeddab"
  38,5,"Aâni ad irr iôebbiten, d Öebbi Yiwen? Ayagi d ayen issewhamen"
  38,6,"Kkren imeqwôanen segsen, nnan: \"elêut, illit d imezgiyen ar iôebbiten nnwen. Ayagi, d ayen iwatan"
  38,7,"Ur nesli i waya, di ddin aneggaru. Ihi, aya, siwa asnulfu"
  38,8,"Day, garane$, d neppa iwumi d irs usmekti\"? Xaîi, nitni di ccekk, $ef usmekti W, mazal ur jeôôben ara aâaqeb iW"
  38,9,"Ne$ sâan lexzayen uêunu n Mass ik, Uzmir, A$eyyat"
  38,10,"Ne$, nnsen tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen? Anef ad alin ihi, s imraren"
  38,11,"Nitni siwa d iâeskôiwen imexsuôen, seg ikabaren"
  38,12,"Zwaren ten id, ar uskiddeb, agdud n Nuê, Âad, Ferâun bu ibudiden"
  38,13,"Tamud, agdud n Luî, At Laika; d widak ay d ikabaren"
  38,14,"Akw, skaddben imazanen, ihi, iwata uâaqeb iW"
  38,15,"Wigi, ad gganin kan ti$ôi yiwet, ur as ippili wallus"
  38,16,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! £iwwel ane$ deg umur nne$, uqbel ass iqeîîiyen"
  38,17,"Eûbeô i wayen d qqaôen. Mmekti d amdan nne£ Dawed, bab n tezmert. Ih, Neppa ippales"
  38,18,"Ih, Nêeppem i idurar ad sbuccuâen yides, tameddit, tafara"
  38,19,"Ifôax mlalen. Akw, i Neppa, ppalsen"
  38,20,"Nesseohed tagelda s, Nefka ias ûûwab, awal iqaâden"
  38,21,"Ma ibbwev ik id usali n yixûimen, mi ulin ar tmezgida"
  38,22,"Mi kecmen ar Dawed, iugad iten. Nnan: \"ur ppagwad, d sin ixûimen, yiwen degne$, ijuô $ef wayev. Eêkem garane$ s tidep, war taneêyaft. Enhu ya$ s abrid umâin"
  38,23,"Ihi, gma yagi, isâa tza u tzat n wulli, nek tixsi yiwet. Inna yi d: kwellef iyi p. Irna yi s wawal"
  38,24,"Inna: \"ni$ idens ik s usuter n texsi inek, a p irnu ar wulli ines. Aîas n yicriken i ippemjuôen, siwa wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, drus nnsen ay llan\". Ifhem Dawed Njeôôeb it kan; iste$feô Mass is, i$li, iîîanez, indem"
  38,25,"Nsemmeê as ayagi. Ih, i neppa, $uône£, amkan n tu$alin aqôib, umâin"
  38,26,"A Dawed, Nerra k, ih, d agensas di tmurt. Ëudd ger imdanen s tidep, ur îîafaô lhawiyya, a k tetlef seg ubrid n Öebbi. Ihi, wid innetlafen seg ubrid n Öebbi, fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê, imi ppun ass iqeîîiyen"
  38,27,"Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di rrayaâ, akken nwan wid ijehlen. A tawa$it n tmes, i wid ijehlen"
  38,28,"Day a Nerr wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, am wid issefsaden di ddunit? Ne$ a Nerr wid ipêezziben am laâôuô"
  38,29,"Tazmamt Nessers ak p id, teôqa, iwakken ad meyyzen issekniyen is, a d mmektin uâqilen"
  38,30,"N$at Dawed s Sliman, amdan ukiys ippalsen"
  38,31,"Mi s d sseknen, tameddit, tigmarin lâali"
  38,32,"inna: \"nek, smenyafe$ tayri n wayla, i usmekti n Mass iw, armi sberbren fellasent"
  38,33,"Erret pent id $uôi\". Igezm asent ivaôen, timegrav"
  38,34,"Ni$, Njeôôeb Sliman; Nessers loeppa af usgeld is. Iu$al indem"
  38,35,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Semmeê iyi, £it iyi s tgelda ur nepûaê yiwen, deffir i. S tidep, Keçç d A$iyyat"
  38,36,"Nenub fellas s wavu. Ipûuvu, s lameô is, d abeêri, s anda i s ihwa"
  38,37,"Ccwaîen akw ibennun, ip$emmisen"
  38,38,"Wiyad pwarzen, s slasel"
  38,39,"Tagi d tikci nne£. Efk ne$ eîîef, war aktili"
  38,40,"Ih, i neppa, $uône£, amkan n tu$alin aqôib, umâin"
  38,41,"Mmekti d amdan nne£ Yub, mi inâaô Mass is: \"nek, iêuza yi Cciîan, s cedda akked uâaqeb"
  38,42,"Aâfes s uvaô ik, wagi d amkan semmven, i tarda u i tissit"
  38,43,"N$at it s twacult is, akked yides tin i p icban, d aêunu s$uône£, d asmekti i uâqilen"
  38,44,"Eddem deg ufus ik taseîîa, ewwet yis ur êennet\". Ni$ Nufa t d aûebôi, d amdan amxallef ippalsen"
  38,45,"Mmekti d imdanen nne£: Ibôahim, Isêaq, Iaâqub. D imawlan n tezmert akked yiéôi"
  38,46,"Ih, Nûeffa ten, s ûûfawa usmekti n Uxxam"
  38,47,"Nitni, $uône£, war ccekk, seg wid iufraren, i Nefren"
  38,48,"Mmekti d: Ismaâil, Lyasaâ, Du-al-Kifl. Akw, seg wid Nefren"
  38,49,"Wagi d asmekti. Ih, i wid ipêezziben, tisin igerzen mavi"
  38,50,leonanat n Âaden. Llin asen tibbura
  38,51,"Ad ttekkin dinna. Ad ssutren degsen; izwayen s lufa, akked tisit"
  38,52,"£uôsen, sut wallen ibran, ppizyiwin"
  38,53,"D wagi i wen ippuwaââden, i wass iqeîîiyen"
  38,54,"D wagi, s tidep, ay d l$it nne£, ur nepfukku"
  38,55,"Akka. Wanag, i iqehhaôen, tisin icemten mavi"
  38,56,"Loahennama, ad degs ô$en; a yir usu"
  38,57,"Akka, ad jeôôben aman ippayzagen, akked wid ipfuêun"
  38,58,"akked wayen nniven i ten icban, d tiyugiwin"
  38,59,"Atan urbaâ i iddehmen yidwen, ur anûuf yissen. Ih, di tmes ad ô$en"
  38,60,"Nnan: \"xaîi, ur anûuf yiswen, kunwi! D kunwi i $ p id iheggan\". A yaxxam adiran"
  38,61,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Sâaddi berdayen aâaqeb n tmes, $ef wid i $ d iheggan aya"
  38,62,"Nnan: \"acu i $ iu$en, ur nwala ara irgazen, i nella nêesb iten seg imcumen mavi"
  38,63,"Day nemsexxeô fellasen, ne$ dergen i wallen"
  38,64,"Ih, aya d tidep, d amqellaâ n at tmes"
  38,65,"Ini: \"nek, d aneddaô kan. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi, Yiwen, Aqehhaô"
  38,66,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, Uzmir Ipsemmiêen"
  38,67,"Ini: \"d asali ameqwôahan"
  38,68,"Kunwi, teooam t"
  38,69,"Ur illi wayen éôi$ $eô le$wat aâlayen meôôa, mi mqellaân"
  38,70,"Ppuweêêa$ d kan, ar nek d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  38,71,"Mi Inna Mass ik i lmalayek: \"Nek ad Xelqe$ amdan, si talaxt"
  38,72,"Mi t Mesle$, Suve$ degs, si ôôuê iW, îinzemt $uôes, s lekni"
  38,73,"Knant akw lmalayek, akken ma llant"
  38,74,"siwa Iblis i izuxxen, illa seg ijehliyen"
  38,75,"Inna: \"A Iblis, w ik igedlen lekni i win Xelqe$ s ifassen iW? Tzuxxev, ne$ telliv seg wid iufraren"
  38,76,"Inna: \"Nek ife$ t. Txelqev iyi si tmes, Txelqev t si talaxt"
  38,77,"Inna: \"Effe$ segs, keçç d imenfi"
  38,78,"Inna: \"fellak xezzu, alamma d ass iqeîîiyen"
  38,79,"Inna: \"A Mass iw, eoo iyi ar ass ideg ara d kkren"
  38,80,"Inna: \"keçç, ih, seg wid Ooi"
  38,81,ar ass n wukud ipwassnen
  38,82,"Inna: \"s tezmert iK, a ten $ewwu$, akken ma llan"
  38,83,siwa imdanen iK izedganen segsen
  38,84,"Inna: \"tidep, d tidep ay Nni"
  38,85,"Ad Acare$ Loahennama yissek, akked wid, segsen, i k ivefôen, akken ma llan"
  38,86,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$ taqdiât af waya. Ur lli$, nek, seg wid ippestaâmilen"
  38,87,"Neppa, s tidep, d asmekti kan i imavalen"
  38,88,"Mi tâadda tallit, war ccekk, a kwen id iawev usali s"
  39,1,"Tarusi n Tezmamt s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  39,2,"Ih, Nessader ak d Tazmamt, s tidep. Ihi, aâbed Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa"
  39,3,"Day maççi i Öebbi laâqida? Wid ippaddamen imawlan, war Neppa, nnan: \"naâbed iten kan, iwakken ad a$ rnun aseqôeb ar Öebbi\". Ih, Öebbi ad Iêudd garasen, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden. Öebbi, war ccekk, ur Inehhu win illan d akeddab, d ajehli"
  39,4,"Lemmer Ib$i Öebbi ad Isâu aqcic, yili Ifren, deg wayen Ixelleq, ayen i S ihwan. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô"
  39,5,"Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Innev Iv i wass, Innev ass i yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur, ad lêun, yal wa, ar lajel ipwassnen. Day Neppa maççi d Uzmir Ipsemmiêen"
  39,6,"Ixelq ikwen si yiwen n lxelq. Irra, segs, tislit is. Issers awen d îam n tyugiwin n lmal. Ixelq ikwen di tâabbuvin n tyimmatin nnwen, lxelq deffir lxelq, di krav n tellisat. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. IneS tagelda, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Amek ihi tugim"
  39,7,"Ma tjehlem, Öebbi ur kwen Iêwao ara. Ur Ipôadi tijehli i imdanen iS. Ma tesnemmrem, a kwen Iôavi. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev; sinna, ar Mass nnwen tu$alin nnwen; ad awen Imel acu txeddmem. Ih, Neppa, Issen i illan deg idmaren"
  39,8,"Amdan, ma iêuza t ccqa, ad inuj ar Mass is, d ucâif $uôes; sinna, ma I$at it s$uôeS, ad ippu ayen i$ef inuj $uôeS, uqbel; ad irr i Öebbi tanudda, ad innetlaf seg ubrid iS. Ini: \"zzhu cwiî di tijehli k, ihi, keçç seg wat tmes"
  39,9,"Day win ippanzen deg iv, ikna u ibedd, ipêebbiô i laxeôt, issaram aêunu n Mass is…? Ini: \"day âadlen wid issnen akked wid ur nessin? Ay d ismektayen, kan, d uâqilen"
  39,10,"Ini: \"a yimdanen iW iumnen, êezzbet i Mass nnwen. Ayen ilhan i wid imaânen di ddunit agi. Tamurt n Öebbi tewsaâ. Ihi, arraz, war aktili, ad ippunefk i iûebôiyen"
  39,11,"Ini: \"nek pwamôe$ d ad âabde$ Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa"
  39,12,"Pwamôe$ d, ad ili$ d amvuâ amenzu"
  39,13,"Ini: \"nek, ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan"
  39,14,"Ini: \"ad âabde$ Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa"
  39,15,"Ihi, âabdet i wen ihwan, war Neppa\". Ini: \"imexsuôen d wid iwedôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra\". Ni$ d tagi ay d taxessaôt n ûûeê"
  39,16,"A$embabu n tmes, sennig sen, wayev seddawat sen. Ayagi, Issagwad yis Öebbi imdanen iS: a yimdanen iW, êezzbet iyI"
  39,17,"Wid ijunben aâbad iôebbiten n tkerkas, u iutuben Öebbi, a ten id ias lfeôê. Ihi, ssefôeê imdanen iW"
  39,18,"i issemêasen i wawal, teddun d ûûam ines. D wigi i Inha Öebbi, d wigi ay d uâqilen"
  39,19,"Day win i$ef ippuseyya ad isâaddi aâaqeb, day a psellkev keçç, win illan di tmes"
  39,20,"Ma d wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad sâun ti$uôfatin, bnant ta sennig ta, isaffen seddawat sent ppazzalen, d lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi ur Ixeîîu i lemâahda"
  39,21,"Ur twalav ara, Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni, Issekcem iten ad sswen akal. Sinna, yissen, a d Issuffe$ im$an n yal ini, ara iu$alen ad isliwen. A ten twaliv d iwôa$en, sinna, a ten Irr d iquôanen. Deg waya, s tidep, asmekti i uâqilen"
  39,22,"Day win iwumi Illi Öebbi, idmaren is, ar wannuz, d$a neppa di tafat s$uô Mass is…? A ssxev n at wulawen iqquôen, ur d smektayen Öebbi! Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  39,23,"Issader ed Öebbi ûûam n wawal. Tazmamt, degs acbi, allus. Ad ccirwen segs igwelman akked wulawen n wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, sinna, igwelman akked wulawen nnsen ad iêninen ar usmekti n Öebbi. D tagi ay d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis, win i S ihwan. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi wa ara t inhun"
  39,24,"Day win ipêezziben, s wudem is, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra…? Ad inin i imednas: \"jeôôbet ayen tkeppbem"
  39,25,"Skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Iusa ten id uâaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin"
  39,26,"Issukk fellasen Öebbi aâaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit; war ccekk, aâaqeb n laxeôt iugar it, lemmer éeôôen"
  39,27,"Ni$ Nefka i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, yal amedya, amar a d mmektin"
  39,28,"Leqwôan s taâôabt, ur degs tiââawji; amar ad êezzben"
  39,29,"Ifka d Öebbi amedya n urgaz icerken akked wid ipmeréan, u argaz di tifrat akked yiwen urgaz. Day âadlen sin imedyaten? Ccekôan i Öebbi. Xaîi, tegwti degsen ur ssinen"
  39,30,"War ccekk, keçç a ppemmtev, nitni ad mmten"
  39,31,"Sinna, kunwi, ass n tnekra, ar Mass nnwen, a ppemqellaâm"
  39,32,"Anwa i idensen sennig win iskaddben af Öebbi, iskaddben tidep ma tusa t id? Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam ijehliyen"
  39,33,"Wid id iusan s tidep, u pputebbten yis, wigi d wid ipêezziben"
  39,34,"Ad sâun ayen b$an, ar Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d arraz iâaôviyen"
  39,35,"Iwakken ad asen Ikkes Öebbi, ayen xedmen adiran mavi; a ten I$it s wayen xeddmen d amxallef"
  39,36,"Day ur Ipqam ara Öebbi amdan iS? La k ssagwaden s wid, war Neppa. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi w ara t inhun"
  39,37,"Win Inha Öebbi, ur illi w ara t itelfen. Ni$ Öebbi d Uzmir, Bab n ppaô"
  39,38,"Ma testeqsav ten: \"anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Ad inin, war ccekk: d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ma twalam wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, day zemren, ma Ib$a yi Öebbi ccqa, ad kksen ccqa S? Ne$, ma Ib$a yi aêunu, ad ssbeîlen aêunu S\"? Ini: \"Iqennaâ iyi Öebbi; fellaS ay ppeklen wid ipkalen"
  39,39,"Ini: \"a yagdud iw! Xedmet akken tennumen, nek la xeddme$\". Deqqal a ppeéôem"
  39,40,"anwa u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, u$uô ara d irs uâaqeb imezgi"
  39,41,"Ih, Nessader ed $uôek, Tazmamt i medden, s tidets. Win ipwanhan, i iman is, win innetlafen, innetlaf kan, mgal is. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen"
  39,42,"Öebbi Ippaddam leôwaê mara mmten, akked wid ur nemmut, deg ives nnsen. Iâatteq wid i$ef Iseyya tameppant, Ippara d wiyav, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ih, deg wayagi, ard issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen"
  39,43,"Ne$ ad ddmen, war Öebbi, imcafâan? Ini: \"i ma ur sâin acemma, ur fhimen"
  39,44,"Ini: \"akw ccafuâa n Öebbi. IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Sinna, $uôeS ara tu$alem"
  39,45,"Mara d Ipwadder Öebbi Yiwen, ad zemven wulawen n wid ur numin ara s laxeôt. Ma pwadren d wid, war Neppa, imiren nitni ad ceôêen"
  39,46,"Ini: \"a Öebbi! Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, Amusnaw n wayen iffren d wayen ivehôen, d Keçç ara Iêudden ger imdanen iK, $ef wayen llan mgarraden"
  39,47,"Wid idensen, lemmer nnsen ayen akw i illan di tmurt, rnu yas am neppa, ur ten id ifeddu, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra. Ad asen d iban, s$uô Öebbi, ayen i$ef ur bnin"
  39,48,"Ad asen d banent tucmitin kesben, ad asen innev wayen i$ef ttahan"
  39,49,"Ma iêuza umdan ccqa, ad a£ d inâaô. Sinna, ma Nezger tacvaî nne£ fellas, ad yini: \"tusa yi d kan si tmusni\". Xaîi! D ajeôôeb, maca aîas degsen ur ssinen"
  39,50,Ni$ nnan t id imezwura nnsen. Acu i sen d ibbwi wayen keppben
  39,51,"Iwwet iten wayen kesben n tucmitin. Wid idensen, seg wigi, a ten iwwet wayen kesben n tucmitin. Ur zmiren ad sfunngen"
  39,52,"Day ur éôin ara ar Öebbi Ip$iti win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen? Ih, deg waya, ard issekniyen i ugdud iumnen"
  39,53,"Ini: \"a yimdanen iw i ipêawalen mgal iman nnsen! Ur ppayset aêunu n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê akw ibekkaven. Ih, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  39,54,"Steôoâet i Mass nnwen, anzet aS, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, d$a ula ikwen isellken"
  39,55,"Ddut d ûûam n wayen i wen d irsen, s$uô Mass nnwen, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, deqzalla, kunwi ur tebnim"
  39,56,"u a d yini ôôuê: \"a ssexv iw, $ef wayen stehza$ ar loiha n Öebbi! Lli$, s tidep, seg wid ittihin"
  39,57,"Ne$ a d yini: \"lemmer iyi Inha Öebbi, yili lli$ seg wid ipêezziben"
  39,58,"Ne$ a d yini mara iwali aâaqeb: \"lemmer iyi illi wallus, ad ili$ si lâuûam"
  39,59,"Xaîi! Usan k id issekniyen iW, teskaddbev ten, tzuxxev, telliv seg ijehliyen"
  39,60,"Ass n tnekra, a pwaliv berrikit wudmawen n wid id igren tikerkas af Öebbi. Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam imzuxiyen"
  39,61,"Ad Isellek Öebbi wid iêezzben; ar rebêen. Ur ten ikkat wugur, ur $webbnen"
  39,62,Öebbi Ixleq yal cci. Neppa d Awkil n yal cci
  39,63,"IneS tsura n tmurt akked igenwan. Wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen"
  39,64,"Ini: \"day ad yi tamôem ad âabde$, war Öebbi, a wid ur nessin"
  39,65,"Ni$ iusa k id uweêêi, u $eô wid i k izwaren. Ma tcurkev, ad mêun igiten ik, a ppiliv seg imexsuôen"
  39,66,Xaîi! Aâbed Öebbi. Ili seg wid isnemmiren
  39,67,"Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Akw tamurt, ass n tnekra, di tumeét iS. Igenwan ad nnefvasen deg ufus iS ayeffus. Gedha s yiS! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken"
  39,68,"Aûuvu di lbuq: ad ixsef i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, kkes ed i S ihwan i Öebbi. Aûuvu nniven: nitni a d kkren pmuqulen"
  39,69,"A pfeooeo tmurt, si tafat n Mass is. A d ters Tezmamt, a d awin lambiyya akked inagan. Ad âaddin di ccôaâ, s tidep, ur pwadensen"
  39,70,"Yal yiwen ad i$ellet ayen ixdem. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, d acu xeddmen"
  39,71,"Ad pwanehôen wid ijehlen, d igrawen, ar Loahennama. Mi bbwven $uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: \"day ur kwen in usan ara imazanen, segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen n Mass nnwen, nedôen kwen af temlilit n wass nnwen agi\"? A d inin: \"Ih. Maca, ad iûaô wawal uâaqeb, af ijehliyen"
  39,72,"A d inin: \"kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama! Degs, wekkôet\". Ay d ucmit uxxam n imzuxiyen"
  39,73,"Wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad pwanehôen ar Loennet, d igrawen. Mi bbwven $uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: \"tifrat fellawen, tgerzem; kecmet ep, twekkôem"
  39,74,"Ad inin: \"ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Issawven lemâahda S. Ifka ya$ tamurt d lweôt; a nili, di Loennet, anda i $ ihwa. A yarraz asaâdi n wid ixeddmen lxiô"
  39,75,"A pwaliv lmalayek zzint ed i usgeld, sbuccuâent s ccekôan Mass nnsent. Iâadda ccôaâ garasen, s tidep. Ad inin: \"a neckeô Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  40,1,Ëm
  40,2,"Tarusi n Tezmamt, s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Amusnaw"
  40,3,"Ipsemmiêen tuccva, Iqeblen nndama, Ipâaqaben s teqseê, Bab n terkunt. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £uôeS taggara"
  40,4,"Siwa wid ijehlen i ipnamaren $ef issekniyen n Öebbi. Ur k ip$uôôu ucali nnsen, di tmurt"
  40,5,"Uqbel nitni, agdud n Nuê, akked ikabaren deffir sen, skaddben. Yal lois iclaâ ad ixvef amazan is. Ipnamar s tkerkas, iwakken, s yissent, ad iveggeô tidep. Ëekme$ ten. A tiyta W imiren"
  40,6,"Akka iûaô wawal n Mass ik, af wid ijehlen. Nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes"
  40,7,"Tid irefden asgeld, akked tid i s izzin, sbuccuâen s ccekôan Mass nnsent, umnent yiS. Ssuturent ad pwasemmêen wid iumnen: \"a Mass nne$! Terriv yal cci d aêunu, u d tamusni. Semmeê i wid isteôoâen u ddan d ubrid iK; Sellek iten seg uâaqeb n wu$ud"
  40,8,"A Mass nne$! Ssekcem iten ar leonanat n Âaden, i Tâahdev, i nitni, u i iâaôviyen seg ibabaten nnsen, tilawin nnsen, tarwa nnsen. Keçç, ih, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  40,9,"Aâteq iten si tucmitin. Win Tâatqev, assen, si tucmitin, ni$ Têunev fellas. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  40,10,"Ad pwanecden wid ijehlen: \"taâdawt n Öebbi te$leb taâdawt bbwaygarawen. Mi tepwanecdem ar liman, tugim"
  40,11,"A d inin: \"a Mass nne$! Ten$iv a$ berdayen, Tessidrev a$ berdayen. Nqaôô s ibekkaven nne$. Day illa ubrid n tuff$a"
  40,12,"Akka, imi mara ipwanâaô Öebbi Yiwen, kunwi tjehlem. Mara S pcaraken, kunwi tumnem. Aêuddu ar Öebbi Aâlayen, Ameqwôan"
  40,13,"D Neppa i wen Issnaâtan issekniyen iS. Issadar awen d l$it, seg igenni. Siwa win isteôoiâen, id ismektayen"
  40,14,"Nujet $uô Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa, xas ugin ijehliyen"
  40,15,"Aâlayen nnig idurra, Bab n usgeld, Ippak ôôuê s lameô iS, i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, iwakken ad indeô af wass umlili"
  40,16,"ass ideg ara d awven, ur illi wayen iffren, degsen, i Öebbi. W ip ilan tgelda, assen? D Öebbi, Yiwen, Aqehhaô"
  40,17,"Ass ideg ara ippuqeîîi yal iman $ef wayen ikseb; ur ippili ddens assen. Ih, Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi"
  40,18,"Nabi ten af ass aqôib, ideg ulawen ad rewlen s igerjumen, ad qebôen. Ur ippilli i imednas, uêbib ne$ amcafaâ, iwumi ara ssemêessen"
  40,19,"Issen nncub n yiéôi, akked wayen teffren idmaren"
  40,20,"Öebbi Iferru s tidep. Wid ipnujun ar war Neppa, ur qeîîun acemma. Ih, Öebbi d Win Isellen, Ipwalin"
  40,21,"Day ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten tazmert, akked lateô, di tmurt. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi, ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Ur asen illi umêareb, mgal Öebbi"
  40,22,"Akka, acku ppasen $uôsen, imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, u nitni jehlen. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab uâaqeb uqsiê"
  40,23,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa s issekniyen nne£, s udabu iberrzen"
  40,24,"ar Ferâun, Haman, akked Qaôun. Nnan: \"d aseêêar, d akeddab"
  40,25,"Mi sen d iusa, s tidep s $uône£, nnan: \"en$et arrac n wid iumnen yides, ssidret tilawin nnsen\". Tandit ijehliyen siwa di ttelfan"
  40,26,"Inna Ferâun: \"anfet iyi ad n$e$ Musa, xas ad inuj ar Mass is. Ugade$, nek, ad ibeddel ddin nnwen, ne$ a d issekcem lefsad di tmurt"
  40,27,"Inna Musa: \"nek, ad iyi Iûûeô Mass iw u Mass nnwen, si yal amzuxi, ur numin s wass uqeîîi"
  40,28,"Inna urgaz lmumen, i iffren liman is, si twacult n Ferâun: \"day a ppen$em argaz, imi d iqqaô: Mass iw d Öebbi, u irna ibbwi yawen d abeggen, s$uô Mass nnwen? Ma iskaddeb, lkedb is fellas. Ma issawel tidep, a kwen iêaz kra seg wayen ikwen issagwad. Öebbi ur Inehhu amaâfun iskiddiben"
  40,29,"A yagdud iw! Assa, nnwen tagelda, tufrarem di tmurt. W ad a$ isellken si tiyta n Öebbi, ma tusa ya$ d\"? Inna d Ferâun: \"i wen ssekne$ ayen kan wala$; s anda i kwen nehhu$, siwa ar ubrid imaânen"
  40,30,"Inna d win iumnen: \"a yagdud iw! Nek, ugade$ fellak tin n wass ikabaren"
  40,31,"akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, akked wid i ten id ivefôen. Öebbi ur Ib$a ara ddens i imdanen"
  40,32,"A yagdud iw! Nek ugade$, ay kwen ippa$en, ass umnamar"
  40,33,ass ideg ara trewlem ar deffir. Ur awen illi umêareb mgal Öebbi. Ur illi nnahi i win Itlef Öebbi
  40,34,"Ni$ iusa kwen id Yusef, zik, s ubeggen. Tezgam di ccekk, $ef wayen i wen d ibbwi. Armi immut, tennam: \"ur d Ippazen ara Öebbi amazan, deffir es, d awez$i\". Akka i Itellif Öebbi amaâfun amcekki"
  40,35,"Wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, nezzeh ara ten i$unfu Öebbi, akked wid iumnen. Akka ara Icemmaâ Öebbi, yal ul amzuxi, aâfrit"
  40,36,"Inna Ferâun: \"a Haman, bnu yi lbeôo, amar ad awve$ ar iberdan"
  40,37,"iberdan igenwan. Ad ali$ ar Öebbi n Musa. Nek êesbe$ t d akeddab\". Akka i s ippucebbeê i Ferâun, igi s ucmit. Ippuveôôef seg ubrid. Tandit n Ferâun, siwa taxeûûart"
  40,38,"Inna d win iumnen: \"a yagdud iw! Ddu yidi, a k nhu$ s abrid umâin"
  40,39,"A yagdud iw! Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, d zzhu kan; wanag laxeôt d axxam n leqôaô"
  40,40,"Win ixedmen tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi, kan, s tin i p icban. Wid ixedmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta, u nitni umnen, widak ad kecmen Loennet; din, ad aten $iten, war aktili"
  40,41,"A yagdud iw! Acu iyi bbwin, a kwen neccde$ ar leslak; kunwi, a yi tneccdem ar tmessi"
  40,42,"A yi tneccdem ad aâûu$ Öebbi, ad aS carke$ ayen ur ssine$. Nek, neccde$ kwen ar Uzmir Ipsemmiêen"
  40,43,"War ccekk, ayen u$uô a yi tneccdem, ur as iwata unuju di ddunit, u di laxeôt. Ih, tu$alin nne$ ar Öebbi. Imaâfan ard at tmes"
  40,44,A d tesmektim ayen i wen qqaôe$. Öôay iw fki$ t i Öebbi. Ni$ Öebbi Ipwali imdanen
  40,45,"Isellek it Öebbi si tucmitin i undin. I$wellef lois n Ferâun, s uâaqeb iugaren wiyav"
  40,46,"times. Ad pwafessren degs, ûûbeê, tameddit. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir: \"ekcem, a lois n Ferâun, aâaqeb uwâiô mavi"
  40,47,"Mara ppemqellaâen di tmes, ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: \"ni$ nella nedda yidwen. Ma tzemrem, kunwi, ad a$ tesneqsem cwiî, si tmes"
  40,48,"A d inin imzuxiyen: \"aql a$, akw, degs. S tidep, Öebbi Iêudd ger imdanen"
  40,49,"Ad inin wid illan di tmes, i iâessasen n Loahennama: \"naâôet Mass nnwen, ad a$ Issifes ibwass uâaqeb"
  40,50,"Ad inin: \"day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen nnwen, s ubeggen\"? Ad inin: \"ih\". Ad inin: \"naâret\"! Ar ttelfan, kan, tanaârit ijehliyen"
  40,51,"War ccekk, a Nsellek imazanen nne£, akked wid iumnen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u deg wass ideg ara d bedden inagan"
  40,52,"ass ideg ur infaâ uste$feô imednas. Ad pwaxzun, ad zed$en deg uxxam ucmit mavi"
  40,53,"Ni$ Nefka, i Musa, nnhaya. Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt d lweôt"
  40,54,"D nnhaya, u d asmekti i uâqilen"
  40,55,"Eûbeô. Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep. Ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, tameddit, taûebêit"
  40,56,"Ih, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, d tem$weô kan i illan deg idmaren nnsen; ur as ssawven. Ggani Öebbi, Neppa, s tidep, Isell, Ipwali"
  40,57,"Ih, lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan iugar lxelq n imdanen, maca aîas n imdanen ur éôin"
  40,58,"Ur iaâdil ara uder$al akked win ipwalin, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, akked bu tucmitin. Cwiî id tesmektayem"
  40,59,"Ihi, imir a d ias, ur illi ccekk fellas, maca tegwti n imdanen ur uminen"
  40,60,"Inna Mass nnwen: \"naâret iyI, ad awen d Jawbe$. Wanag wid igelzen aâbed iW, ad kecmen Loahennama, d imedlulen"
  40,61,"Öebbi i wen Irran iv, i ureyyeê degs, ass i tmu$li. Öebbi, ih, d Bab n lfevl i imdanen, maca tegwti n imdanen, ur snemmiren"
  40,62,"D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ixleq yal cci, ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Ihi, acimi tezzim akin"
  40,63,Akka ay wexxôen wid iugin issekniyen n Öebbi
  40,64,"Öebbi i wen Irran tamurt d leqôaô, igenni d ssqef; ikwen Imeslen. Iûeggem udem nnwen. I$at ikwen s wayen ilhan. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  40,65,"Neppa d Amuddir, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, naâôet eP, s lâaqida i Neppa. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  40,66,"Ini: \"nek, ipwakkes iyi uâbad n wid tnaârem war Öebbi, mi yi d iusa ubeggen, s$uô Mass iw. Pwamôe$ d, ad anze$ i Mass imavalen"
  40,67,"Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen seg wakal; sinna, si tiqqit; sinna, seg urgen; sinna, Issuffe$ ikwen id d igwerdan; sinna, a ppim$uôem; sinna, a ppu$alem d im$aôen. Kra segwen, pmeppaten uqbel. Iwakken a ppawvem ar lajel ipwassnen. Amendeô ma a pfehmem"
  40,68,"D Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. Ma Iseyya d lameô, ad as Yini kan: \"ili\"! Ad yili"
  40,69,"Day ur twalav ara amek ssuff$en i ubrid, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi"
  40,70,"Wid iskaddben Tazmamt, akked wayen i$ef id Nuzen imazanen nne£, deqqal ad éôen"
  40,71,"Mara pwazu$ôen, s teqlavin d slasel"
  40,72,"ar waman ippayzagen; sinna, ar tmes, ad pwaveggôen"
  40,73,"sinna, ad asen inin: \"anda t wayen tepcarakem"
  40,74,"war Öebbi\"? A d inin: \"dergen fella$. Xaîi! Ur illi wayen u$uô nepnuju, zik\". Akka i Itellif Öebbi ijehliyen"
  40,75,"Akka, $ef wayen tzehhum di tmurt, ur teklalem, akked wayen tqebêem"
  40,76,"Kecmet Loahennama, si tebbura; degs twekkôem. Ay dir tanezdu$t imzuxiyen"
  40,77,"Eûbeô, war ccekk, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ad ak Nessken kra n wayen i sen Nâahed, ne$ a Neddem ôôuê ik. £uône£ ara d u$alen"
  40,78,"Ni$ Nuzen ed imazanen uqbel ik. £ef kra segsen, Neêka yak d. £ef kra nniven, ur ak d Neêka ara. Ur iwata ara i umazan, a d iawi assekni, siwa ma s tsriê n Öebbi. Ma iusa d lameô n Öebbi, aseyyi s tidep. Ad xesôen, imiren, laâôuô"
  40,79,Öebbi i wen Ifkan lmal i rekba nnwen. Segsen teppeppem
  40,80,"Degsen, i kunwi, aba$uô akked agwav ar wayen id ssuturen idmaren nnwen. Fellasen, akw f ssfinat, teppâabbim"
  40,81,Issenâat awen d issekniyen iS. Anwi issekniyen n Öebbi ara tnekôem
  40,82,"Day ur nudan ara tamurt ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten akken îîuqten, ifen ten tazmert akked lateô di tmurt. Ulay sen d ibbwi wayen la keppben"
  40,83,"Mi ten id usan imazanen nnsen s ubeggen, feôêen s tmusni i illan $uôsen. Izzi fellasen wayen i$ef ppemsexxiôen"
  40,84,"Mi walan tamnirt nne£, nnan: \"numen s Öebbi Yiwen, nveggeô ayen i nella ncurek aS"
  40,85,"Ur izmir ara a ten infaâ liman nnsen, mi walan tamnirt nne£. D tannumi n Öebbi, si zik, i imdanen iS. Akka ay xesôen ijehliyen"
  41,1,Ëm
  41,2,Tarusi s$uô Uênin Ipêunun
  41,3,"Tazmamt, feûûlen issekniyen is; Leqwôan s taâôabt, i ugdud issnen"
  41,4,"ipbecciôen, ineddôen. Tegwti degsen numren, d$a ur sellen"
  41,5,"Nnan: \"ulawen nne$ ddurin i wayen i$eô la $ tneccdev; di tmejjin nne$: tiâéegt; garane$ yidek: sîeô. Ihi, exdem, nekwni la nxeddem"
  41,6,"Ini: \"nek d amdan kan, am kunwi. Weêêan iyi d kan ar Öebbi nnwen, d Öebbi Yiwen. Sweqmet $uôeS, ssutret aS ssmaê\". A tawa$it n imcurak"
  41,7,"wid ur nepzekki, u nitni nekôen laxeôt"
  41,8,"Ih, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan: arraz ur nepnegzay"
  41,9,"Ini: \"kunwi aql akwen la tnekôem Win Ixelqen tamurt, di sin wussan. La S tepparam nned. Wagi d Mass imavalen"
  41,10,"Irra degs idurar sufella. Iôqa p, Iwzen degs tagwella s, di kué wussan. Akka i wid isteqsayen"
  41,11,"Sinna, Izzi ar igenni i illan d abbu. Inna yas, u i tmurt: \"aset ed, teb$am ne$ tugim\"! Nnan: \"a n nas, d imvuâen"
  41,12,"Iseyya ten d ûa igenwan, di sin wussan. Iweêêa lameô is, i yal igenni. Ncebbeê igenni aqôib mavi, s teftilin, u d laânaya. D aya ay d Iqeddeô n Uzmir, Amusnaw"
  41,13,"Ma numren, ini: \"ssagwde$ kwen s ssiâqa, am ssiâqa n Âad u Tamud"
  41,14,"Mi ten id usan imazanen, zdat sen, u deffir sen: \"ur âabdet, siwa Öebbi\"! Nnan: \"lemmer i S ihwi i Mass nne$, a d Issers lmalayek. Nekwni, ihi, nenkeô ayen i s id teppuceggâam"
  41,15,"Wanag Âad, sme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, ur klalen. Nnan: \"anwa i $ i$elben di tezmert\"? Day ur walan ara, Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, I$elb iten di tezmert? Llan la nekôen issekniyen nne£"
  41,16,"Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, deg ussan imevyaôen, iwakken a Nessukk fellasen, aâaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Aâaqeb n laxeôt, war ccekk, isdullu kteô. Ur asen ippili umâiwen"
  41,17,"Wanag Tamud, Nebbwi ten d ubrid. Smenyafen tider$elt i nnhaya. Tewwet iten ssiâqa n uâaqeb issrusun, ilmend n wayen keppben"
  41,18,"Nsellek wid iumnen, i illan pêezziben"
  41,19,"Ass ideg ara ssemlilen ar tmessi, icenga n Öebbi, nitni ad pwajemmlen"
  41,20,"Alamma, mara awven $uôes, ad cehhden fellasen, $ef wayen xeddmen, imeééu$en nnsen, allen nnsen, d igwelman nnsen"
  41,21,"Ad inin i igwelman nnsen: \"acimi id tcuhhdem fella$\"? A d inin: \"Issenîeq a$ d Öebbi, id Issentaqen yal cci. Neppa, Ixelq ikwen tikelt tamezwarut, u $uôeS ara tu$alem"
  41,22,"Ur tezmirem ara a ppeffrem, ur cehhden fellawen imeééu$en nnwen, allen nnwen, akked igwelman nnwen. Maca, t$ilem ur Iéeô ara Öebbi, aîas n wayen txeddmem"
  41,23,"Akka ameyyez nnwen $ef Mass nnwen. Isqucc ikwen, tegwram d d imexsuôen"
  41,24,"Xas ûebôen, di tmes ara zed$en. Ma ssutren ssmaê, ur llin d wid ara ipwaqeblen"
  41,25,"Nefka yasen imeddukwal i sen icebbêen ayen illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Iûaô fellasen wawal ger leoyus n yimdanen akw n leonun, i i$aben, uqbel nnsen. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen"
  41,26,"Nnan wid ijehlen: \"ur ssemêaset i Leqwôan agi. Ssekret fellas, ta$wegwa, ahat a prebêem"
  41,27,"A Nessukk $ef wid ijehlen, aâaqeb uqsiê. A ten Nqeîîi sennig wayen xeddmen"
  41,28,"D wagi ay d aqeîîi icenga n Öebbi: times; i nitni degs axxam n lebda; d aqeîîi, imi la nekôen issekniyen nne£"
  41,29,"Ad inin, wid ijehlen: \"a Mass nne$! Essken a$ wid i $ i$elîen, d loenn ne$ d amdan; a ten neôkev, ad u$alen seg wid indellen mavi"
  41,30,"Ih, wid innan: \"Mass nne$ d Öebbi\", sinna, nudan lewqama, a d rsent $uôsen lmalayek: \"ur ppagwadet, ur $webblet; ppubeccôet s Loennet i wen ippuwaââden"
  41,31,"Nekwni d imawlan nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit u di laxeôt. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen i cedhant teôwiêin nnwen. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen tessutrem"
  41,32,"D tarusi s$uô Win Ipsemmiêen, Ipêunun"
  41,33,"Anwa yifen awal umâin n win inaâôen Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id innan: \"nek, ih, seg imvuâen"
  41,34,"Ur iaâdil ise$ akked tucmip. Err ip akin, s wayen ip yifen. Ma tella cceêna, garak d yiwen, ad iu$al d aêbib i k iêemmlen"
  41,35,"Ur teppunefk siwa i wid iûebbôen. Ur teppunefk, siwa i bu sser abarar"
  41,36,"Ma iccacev ak Cciîan tuccva, ssuter laânaya n Öebbi. Ih, Neppa d win Isellen, d Amusnaw"
  41,37,"Seg issekniyen iS, ass akked yiv, iîij akked waggur. Ur kennut ara i yiîij, ne$ i waggur. Knut i Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, ma d Neppa ay tâabbdem"
  41,38,"Ma zuxxen, ihi, wid illan ar Mass ik, sbuccuâen T iv akked wass, ur âaggun"
  41,39,"Seg issekniyen iS: a pwaliv, keçç, akal iqquô; lemmer ad as Nesse$li aman, a d iakwi, ad icuff. Win it id Issadren, d Win ara d Issidren lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa, Izmer i yal cci"
  41,40,"Ih, wid issexûaôen issekniyen nne£, ur drigen fellane£. Menyif win ara ipwaveggôen ar tmes, ne$ win ara iasen di laman, ass n tnekra? Xedmet ayen i wen ihwan. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  41,41,"Akka, wid inekôen asmekti, mi ten id iusa, u neppat ard Tazmamt tuzmirt"
  41,42,"Ur d iusi le$wlav zdat es, ne$ deffir es. D tarusi s$uô Bab n ûûwab, Amaâzuz"
  41,43,"Awal i k id iusan, d win kan id iusan imazanen, uqbel ik. Mass ik, ih, ard Bab n ssmaê, d Bab uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  41,44,"Lemmer Nerri Leqwôan s tmeslayt tabeôôanit, a d inin: \"lemmer feûûlen issekniyen iS s wawal abeôôani, u s taâôabt\"? Ini: \"neppa, i wid iumnen, d nnhaya u d ccafuâa. Wid ur numin ara, âaégent tmejjin nnsen. Neppa, i nitni, d tider$elt. Widak pwanecden seg umkan ibaâden"
  41,45,"Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uô Mass ik, yili tefra garasen. Nitni, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel"
  41,46,"Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win iccven, mgal iman is. Mass ik ur Idennis ara imdanen"
  41,47,"£uôeS ay tella tmusni n yimir. Ur d iteffe$ uzway si txeddact is, ur treffed nnta tadist, ur tepparew, siwa ma Iéôa. Ass ideg ar asen Isiwel: \"anda ten icriken iW\"? A d inin: \"ad aK nini, ur illi garane$ unagi"
  41,48,"Iooa ten wayen u$uô pnujun zik. Fehmen, ur asen illi ssôan"
  41,49,"Ur ifeccel ara umdan di tuppra n lxiô. Ma inul it lqeôê, ad iayes, ad innu$ben"
  41,50,"Ma Nseêess as aêunu nne£, deffir ccqa i t iêuzan, war ccekk, ad yini: \"ayagi inu. Ur cukke$ ara imir a d ias. Ma bbwve$ s afus n Mass iw, ad afe$ $uôeS ûûam\". Ih, a Nbeggen ayen xedmen, i wid ijehlen, u, ih, ad Nsâaddi fellasen aâaqeb iwaâôen"
  41,51,"Ma N$at amdan ad iwexxeô, izzi akin. Ma iêuza t lêif, ad ipnuju, irennu"
  41,52,"Ini: \"tmeyyzem ma iusa d s$uô Öebbi, u kunwi tnekôem t\"? Anwa innetlafen sennig win illan di ticuîna tu$miqt"
  41,53,"Ad asen Nessken issekniyen nne£ di tmurt akked igenwan, u deg iman nnsen, alamma pputebbten ar neppa d tidep. Day ur Iqadd ara Mass ik mi Neppa, war ccekk, d Anagi n yal cci"
  41,54,"Day, s tidep, cukken timlilit d Mass nnsen? Day Neppa, s tidep, ur Izzi ara i yal cci"
  42,1,Ëm
  42,2,Âsq
  42,3,"Akka i Iweêêa i keçç, akked wid ik id izwaren, Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  42,4,"IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Neppa, d Aâlayen, d Ameqwôahan"
  42,5,"Qôib ad ccergen igenwan seg ixfawen nnsen, mara d lhint lmalayek deg usbuccaâ s ccekôan n Mass nnsent, u ssuturent ad pwassemêen kra illan di tmurt. War ccekk, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  42,6,"Wid irran imawlan, war Neppa, Iquôaâ ten Öebbi. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen"
  42,7,"Akka ay k n Nweêêa Leqwôan, s taâôabt, iwakken a pnedôev tayimmap n temdinin, akked wayen i s d izzin; a pnedôev af ass n temlilit, ur degs ccekk; arbaâ di Loennet, arbaâ deg ujajiê"
  42,8,"Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Izdukkel iten d yiwen n lois. Maca, ad Issekcem win i S ihwan ar uêunu S. Imednas, ur sâin bab ne$ asettaô"
  42,9,"Ne$ rran imawlan, war Neppa. Öebbi d Neppa ay d Bab, d Neppa i Issidiren lmeggtin, d Neppa i Izemren i yal cci"
  42,10,"Ayen akw i$ef temgarradem, aêuddu s ar Öebbi. Akka Öebbi, Mass iw; fellaS ppekle$, $eô Neppa ay steôoiâe"
  42,11,"Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan. Seg iman nnwen Irra yawen tiyugiwin; si lmal nnwen, tiyugiwin. Isfukti kwen yisent. Ur illi wayen i T icban. Neppa Issel, Ipwali"
  42,12,"IneS tisura n tmurt akked igenwan. Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, Iwezzen. Ih, Neppa Issen yal cci"
  42,13,"Issers awen d, di ddin, ayen i$ef Iweûûa Nuê. Ayen i k Nweêêa, d ayen i$ef Nweûûa Ibôahim, Musa, akked Âisa: \"sbeddet ddin, ur ppemgarradet fellas\". èÈÈéay, i imcurak, wayen u$uô la ten tneccdev. Öebbi Ippawi $uôeS, win i S ihwan; Inehhu $uôeS, win isteôoiâen"
  42,14,"Ur mfaôaqen armi ten id tusa tussna. Ppemvuddun. Lemmer ur d izwar wawal s$uô Mass ik $ef lmijal ipwassnen, yili myefran. Ih, wid iweôten Tazmamt deffir sen, haaten, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel"
  42,15,"Ilmend n waya, enced, ssewqem akken i tepwamôev, ur teddu d cchawi nnsen. Ini: \"umne$ s wayen id Issader Öebbi n Tira. Pwamôe$ d ad wezne$ garawen. Öebbi d Mass nne$, u d Mass nnwen. I nekwni igiten nne$, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppili nnmara garane$. Öebbi ad a$ Issemlil. Tu$alin $uôeS"
  42,16,"Wid ipnamaren af Öebbi, deffir wagwav n loawab $uôsen, ur teswi nnmara nnsen, ar Mass nnsen. Fellasen zzâaf, fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê"
  42,17,"Öebbi id Issadren Tazmamt, s tidep, akked lmizan. W ad ak imlen, ahat imir iqeôb ed"
  42,18,"Ëaren $uôes wid ur numin ara yis. Ma d wid iumnen, ugaden t; éôan ar neppa d tidep. Ih, wid icukken deg imir, haaten, war ccekk, di ttelfan u$miq"
  42,19,"Öebbi d Laîif i imdanen iS. Ip$iti win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  42,20,"Win ib$an tayerza n laxeôt, ad as Nernu di tyerza ines. Win ib$an tayerza n ddunit, ad as Nefk segs. Ur as illi umur di laxeôt"
  42,21,"Ne$ sâan icriken, sse$ôen ten di ddin ur Iqbil Öebbi? Lemmer ur d izwir ara wawal n ufraz, a p fru garasen. I imednas, war ccekk, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  42,22,"A pwaliv imednas feqâen ilmend n wayen kesben, u neppa iddehm ed fellasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di tebêirin n leonanat. Nnsen i sen ihwan $uô Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d lfevl ameqwôan"
  42,23,"D wagi is Ipbecciô Öebbi imdanen iS, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$ taqdiât, af waya, siwa lmaênana i llezm nnwen\". Win ixedmen ise$, ad as Nernu degs lehhu. Öebbi, ih, Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt"
  42,24,"Ne$ a d inin: \"isnulfa d tikerkas af Öebbi\". Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, ad Icemmaâ ul ik. S wawal iS, ad Isqucc Öebbi tikerkas, ad Iêeqqeq tidep. Ih, Neppa Iéôa tababnit n idmaren"
  42,25,D Neppa i Iqeblen nndama n yimdanen iS. Ipsemmiê tucmitin. Issen ayen txeddmem
  42,26,"Issemêas i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb uqsiê"
  42,27,"Ma Issuget Öebbi l$it i imdanen iS, ad be$wven di tmurt. Maca, Issrusu d, s lmizan, ayen i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Ippuxebbeô $ef imdanen iS, Ipwali ten"
  42,28,"D Neppa id Isse$layen ageffur mara aysen. Iweppaâ aêunu S. Neppa d Bab, d Amaâzuz"
  42,29,"Seg issekniyen iS, lxelq n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan n lewêuc, degsen. Izmer Neppa, ma ihwa yaS, a ten id Issemlil"
  42,30,"Kra n tiyta ikwen iwwten, siwa ayen d bbwin ifassen nnwen. Aîas i Ipsemmiê"
  42,31,"Ur tezmirem a ppesfunngem di tmurt. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne$ asettaô"
  42,32,"Seg issekniyen iS, ssfinat di yill, amzun d idurar"
  42,33,"Ma ihwa yaS ad Issens avu, ad êebsent, d tusbivin sufella s. War ccekk, ayagi d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren"
  42,34,Ne$ a ten Issenger ilmend n wayen kesben. Aîas i Ipsemmiê
  42,35,"Ad éôen wid ipnamaren $ef issekniyen nne£, ar ur asen illi ssôan"
  42,36,"Ayen akw i wen ippunefken n wayla, d zzhu n tmeddurt di ddunit. Ayen illan ar Öebbi, yif it; ad idum kteô, i wid iumnen, ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen"
  42,37,"wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen, akked lâaô, u ssurufen i wid i ten isserfan"
  42,38,"wid id ipjawaben i Mass nnsen, péallan, ppemcawaôen $ef lameô nnsen, pseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at"
  42,39,"wid, ma iusa ten lbe$wv, ad qablen"
  42,40,"Aqeîîi n tucmip, d tucmip i p icban. Win isemmêen, issweqmen, arraz is ar Öebbi. Neppa, ih, ur Iêemmel ara imednas"
  42,41,"Ma d wid id irran ppaô mi pwadensen, ur telli tiyta degsen"
  42,42,"Tiyta, kan, deg wid ivuôôen imdanen, iqehôen di tmurt, war ssebba. I wigi, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  42,43,"Ma d win iûebôen, isemmêen, ayagi, s tidep, d aseyyi n lumuô"
  42,44,"Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi bab, deffir eS. A pwaliv imednas, mara éôen aâaqeb, ad inin: \"ma illa ubrid n tu$alin"
  42,45,"A ten twaliv pwafessren fellas, ndellen, ggaren tiî s tugwdi. Ad inin wid iumnen: \"imexsuôen, s tidep, d wid i sxesôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra\". War ccekk, deg uâaqeb imezgi, ara yilin imednas"
  42,46,"Ur asen llin imawlan, ara ten isellken, war Öebbi. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi abrid"
  42,47,"Jawbet i Mass nnwen, uqbel a d ias, s$uô Öebbi, ass ur nepwexxiô. Ur awen ippili ssôan assen, ur tezmirem a pnekôem"
  42,48,"Ma numren, ur k id Nuzen ara d amêareb nnsen. Ay fellak, siwa timenna. Ih, mara Nesêess i umdan aêunu s$uône£, ad ifôeê yis. Mara t tsami tucmip, id bbwin ifassen is, s tidep, amdan ad ikaraâ"
  42,49,"N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Ippak nnta i win i S ihwan, Ippak ddkeô i win i S ihwan"
  42,50,"Ne$ Ipcarak ddkeô d nnta. Isaâqaô win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Issen, Izmer"
  42,51,"Ur ippunefk ara i umdan, ad as Immeslay Öebbi, siwa aweêêi, ne$ deffir ucembir, ne$ a d iazen amazan iwumi ara Iweêêi, s tsriê iS, ayen Ib$a. Ih, Neppa d Aâlayen, d Bab n ûûwab"
  42,52,"Akka ik d Nweêêa ôôuê, si lameô nne£; ur telliv d win issnen d acu p Tezmamt, ne$ liman. Maca, nerra p d tafat. Yis Nenehhu win i £ ihwan, seg imdanen nne£. Ih, d Keçç i ippawin d ubrid uwqim"
  42,53,"abrid n Öebbi, i Isâan i illan di tmurt, i illan deg igenwan. War ccekk, ar Öebbi ay teddun lumuô"
  43,1,Ëm
  43,2,S Tezmamt ipbegginen
  43,3,"Nerra p d Leqwôan s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem"
  43,4,"Neppa, ih, ata $uône£, ar Tyimmap n Tezmamt, d aâlayan, d uûwib"
  43,5,"Day a kwen Nêewwej seg usmekti, imi kunwi d agdud ipêawalen"
  43,6,Acêal id Nuzen d nnbi i imezwura
  43,7,"Ur ten id ippas nnbi, mebla ma mmaâlken fellas"
  43,8,Nemêa wid i ten yifen tazmert. U iûaô umedya imezwura
  43,9,"Ma testeqûav ten: \"anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan\"? A d inin, war ccekk: \"Ixelq iten Uzmir, Amusnaw"
  43,10,"i wen Irran tamurt d dduê; i wen Igan, degs, iberdan - amendeô ma a ppeppwanhum"
  43,11,"id Isse$layen, seg igenni, aman s lmizan - Nessakway yissen tamurt immuten; akka ara d tekkrem"
  43,12,"id Ixelqen akw tiyugiwin, i wen Ifkan, si sfinat akked lmal, ara trekbem"
  43,13,"A pâanncem $ef iârar nnsen; sinna, a d tesmektim l$it n Mass nnwen, mara pâanncem fellasen. A ppinim: \"gedha s Win i d Inuben fella$ s waya, ur t nemlik"
  43,14,"Ih, a nu$al ar Mass nne"
  43,15,"Ëesben ay T iâabden d amur segS. Amdan, s tidep, d anekkaô n ûûeê"
  43,16,"Ne$ day d Iddem tullas seg wayen Ixleq, u Ifren awen d arrac"
  43,17,"Ma ibbwev ed usali yiwen segsen, $ef wayen id ifka d amedya i Uênin, ad yibrik wudem is, ad ikkufer"
  43,18,"ayen d ikren di rrêuê, ur nessifrir anamer"
  43,19,"Ëesben lmalayek, i illan d ixdimen n Uênin, d nnta. Day êevôen i uxlaq nnsent? Tira $ef ccada nnsen; fellasen asteqsi"
  43,20,"Nnan: \"lemmer Irad Uênin, yili ur ten naâbbid\". Ur sâin kra n tmusni $ef waya. Nitni la pxeôôiven kan"
  43,21,"Ne$ Nefka yasen Tazmamt, uqbel Tagi, d$a, degs, îîfen"
  43,22,"Xaîi! Nnan: \"nufa d, ih, imezwura nne$, di laâqida. D$a, nekwni, Nedda di lateô nnsen"
  43,23,"Am akka, ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, aneddaô ar temdint, mebla ma nnan isâiyen is: \"nufa d imezwura nne$ di laâqida. D$a, nedda d lateô nnsen"
  43,24,"Inna: \"i ma bbwi$ awen d nnhaya yifen tin id tufam ar imezwura nnwen\"? Nnan: \"nekwni, ihi, nugwi ayen is id teppuceggâam"
  43,25,"Nerra d ppaô, segsen. Muqel amek tevôa d inekkaôen"
  43,26,"Mi inna Ibôahim i baba s, akked ugdud is: \"nek, ur pkka$ deg wayen la tâabdem"
  43,27,"kkes ed Win iyi d Ixelqen. D Neppa, s tidep, ara iyi Inhun"
  43,28,"Irra t d awal imezgi i texlift is, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  43,29,"U £ate$ ten, nitni akked imezwura nnsen, armi ten id tusa tidep, akked umazan ipbegginen"
  43,30,"Mi ten id tusa tidep, nnan: \"wagi d ssêur, ihi, nekwni nugi t"
  43,31,"Nnan: \"A lemmer id ssadren Leqwôan agi ar urgaz ameqwôaêan n snat temdinin"
  43,32,"Day d nitni i ifeôôqen aêunu n Mass ik? D Nekwni i sen Ifeôôqen tamâict nnsen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u Nessuli kra segsen, tidekkaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken kra, ad sxedmen wiyav. Aêunu n Mass ik yif ayen jemâan"
  43,33,"Lemmer maççi yiwen n lois kan ara yilin imdanen, a Nerr tiseddura n lfeîîa i ixxamen n wid inekôen Aênin, akw i tiseddaôin i$ef ara alin"
  43,34,"i ixxamen nnsen, tibbura; imîeôêen ideg ara élen"
  43,35,"akked uzewweq. Maca, ayagi akw, d astumen i tmeddurt n ddunit. Laxeôt, ar Mass ik, i wid ipêezziben"
  43,36,"Win iooan asmekti n Uênin, ad as Nqelled Cciîan, ad as yili d amsaâef"
  43,37,"Ih, Nitni veôôifen ten seg ubrid, u $ilen ar nitni pwanhan"
  43,38,"Alamma ma iusa d $uône£, inna d: \"ah, awufan gari yidek, amecwaô illan ger ugmuv d wayev\". A yir amsaâef"
  43,39,"Ur kwen infaâ, assa, d awez$i, ma tdensem. Aql akwen tcerkem aâaqeb"
  43,40,"Day a pperrev, keçç, aâeééug ad issel, ne$ a ppenhuv ader$al, akked win illan di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  43,41,"Amar a k id Nekkes, d$a a d Nerr ppaô segsen"
  43,42,"ne$ ak Nessken ayen i sen d Nhegga. £uône£, ih, adabu fellasen"
  43,43,"Ïîef deg wayen i k d ippuweêêan. Keçç, war ccekk, aql ak deg ubrid uwqim"
  43,44,"Wagi, ih, d asmekti i keçç, akked ugdud ik; deqqal fellawen asteqsi"
  43,45,"Steqsi wid id Nuzen, uqbel ik, seg imazanen nne£. Day Nerra, war Aênin, iôebbiten ara âabden"
  43,46,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa s issekniyen nne£, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Inna: \"nek d amazan n Mass imavalen"
  43,47,"Mi sen d ibbwi issekniyen nne£, nitni la ppavsan degsen"
  43,48,"Ur asen Nessenâata assekni, siwa ma i$leb gma s. Nesâadda fellasen aâaqeb, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  43,49,"Nnan: \"a yaseêêar, nâaô a$ Mass ik, s lemâahda i k Ifka. Nekwni ara nepwanhu"
  43,50,"Mi Nessafer aâaqeb fellasen, imiren ad xedâan"
  43,51,"Imdeê Ferâun i ugdud is, inna: \"a yagdud iw, day maççi inu tagelda n Maseô, akked isaffen agi, i ippazalen seddaw i. Day ur twalam ara"
  43,52,"Ne$ nek ur ife$ ara imdelli agi, ur nezmir ad ibeggen"
  43,53,"Acimi ur as qqnen ara imeqyasen n uwôe$, ne$ ur d usint ara yides lmalayek, pwazdan t"
  43,54,"Issefqaâ agdud is. Unzen as. Wigi, ih, d agdud ucmit"
  43,55,"Mi £ zzaâfen, Nerra d ppaô segsen, Ne$meq iten meôôa"
  43,56,"Nerra ten d asmekti u d amedya, i ineggura"
  43,57,"Mi sen d ippunefk mmi s n Meryem, d amedya, agdud ik iugwi t"
  43,58,"Qqaôen: \"ppif iôebbiten nne$, ne$ Neppa\"? Qqaôen ak d akka, i nnmara. Ih, nitni d agdud ipmeôéan"
  43,59,"Neppa d amdan kan. N$at it, Nerra t d amedya i At Isôail"
  43,60,"Lemmer i£ £ ihwi, a Nerr lmalayek di tmurt, deg umkan nnwen"
  43,61,"Neppa, s tidep, d ppbut n yimir. Ur ppilit di ccekk fellas. Ddut yidi; wagi d abrid uwqim"
  43,62,"Ur kwen issefra$ Cciîan! Ih, neppa d acengu nnwen n ûûeê"
  43,63,"Mi n iusa Âisa s issekniyen, inna: \"usi$ d $uôwen s ûûwab, ad awen beggne$ kra, seg wayen i$ef temgarradem. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  43,64,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw u d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eÏ, d wagi ay d abrid uwqim"
  43,65,"Mgarraden ikabaren garasen. A tawa$it n wid idensen, ilmend uâaqeb n wass aqeôêan"
  43,66,"Day a pôaoun imir, ad asen d ias, deqzalla, nitni ur bnin"
  43,67,"Iêbiben, assen, ad u$alen wa d acengu n wa, kkes ed wid ipêezziben"
  43,68,"A yimdanen iW, assa, ur telli tugdi fellawen, ur $webblet"
  43,69,"Wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£, u llan d imvuâen"
  43,70,"Kecmet Loennet, kunwi akked tlawin nnwen, a ppezhum"
  43,71,"Ad asen ddewwiôen, s sniwat n uwôe$, akked ibuqalen; degsen ayen cihwant teôwiêin, ayen iqennâen allen. Kunwi, din, ad twekkôem"
  43,72,"D tagi ay d Loennet i tweôtem, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  43,73,"Degs, i kunwi, aîas n izwayen, segsen a ppeççem"
  43,74,"Ibe$wviyen, s tidep, deg uâaqeb n Loahennama, ad wekkôen"
  43,75,"Ur ipfukku fellasen. Nitni, degs, ad kkufferen"
  43,76,"Ur ten Nednis, maca llan, nitni, d imednas"
  43,77,"Ad necden: \"a Malik, xas ad a$ Iqfeô Mass ik\"! A d ini: \"war ccekk, a pwellfem"
  43,78,"Ni$ Nusa n $uôwen, s tidep, maca tegwti, degwen, keôhen tidep"
  43,79,Ne$ undin ticeôkep. Ula d Nekwni Neppandi
  43,80,"Ne$ $ilen ur Nsell ara i lesrar nnsen, akked tumlin nnsen. Ihi, imceggâen nne£, $uôsen, pparun"
  43,81,"Ini: \"lemmer illi mmi s i Uênin, nek d aâbad amenzu"
  43,82,"Gedha s Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, Mass n usgeld, mgal ayen pxeôôiven"
  43,83,"Anef asen ad nexxôen, ad uraren, alamma mmugren ass nnsen, i sen ippuwaââden"
  43,84,"D Neppa ay d Öebbi deg igenni, d Öebbi di tmurt, u d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw"
  43,85,"Iôqa Win Ilan tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Iéôa melmi ay d imir. £uüôeS, ara tu$alem"
  43,86,"Wid i la naâôen, war Neppa, ur $uôsen kra n ccafuâa, kkes ed inagan n tidep, u nitni éôan"
  43,87,"Ma testeqûav ten anwa iten Ixelqen, a d inin, war ccekk, \"d Öebbi\". Ihi, acimi zzin akin"
  43,88,"Timenna s: \"a Mass iw! Wigi, s tidep, d agdud ur numin"
  43,89,"Wexxeô asen, ini: \"tifrat\"! Deqqal ad éôen"
  44,1,Ëm
  44,2,S Tezmamt ipbegginen
  44,3,"Nessader ip id, ih, deg iv iôqan. Ih, Nekwni, Nella d ineddaôen"
  44,4,"Iban ed degs, yal lameô uûwib"
  44,5,"Lameô s$uône£. Ih, Nekwni Nella d wid Ippaznen"
  44,6,"Aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ih, Neppa Isell, d Amusnaw"
  44,7,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan akked wayen illan garasen, ma tepputebbtem"
  44,8,"Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq. D Mass nnwen, u Mass n lejdud nnwen, imezwura"
  44,9,"Xaîi! Nitni, di ccekk, ppuraren"
  44,10,"Qaôaâ ass, ideg ara d iawi igenni, abbu ipbegginen"
  44,11,Ad i$umm imùdanen. Wagi d aâaqeb aqeôêan
  44,12,A Mass nne$! Kkes a$ aâaqeb; nekwni d lmumnin
  44,13,"Amek ara sâun asmekti, wanag iusa ten id Umazan ipbegginen"
  44,14,"D$a wexxôen as, u nnan: \"d aselmad aôehbani\". ²"
  44,15,"Ma Nessenqes awen cwiî uâaqeb, ihi, kunwi, a ppu$alem ar din"
  44,16,"Ass ideg ara Neédem fellasen, ééedma tabarart, war ccekk, a d Nerr ppaô"
  44,17,"Ni$ Njeôôeb, uqbel nnsen, agdud n Ferâun. Iusa ten id umazan ukyis"
  44,18,"Seddut yidi imdanen n Öebbi; nek, $uôwen, d amazan muman"
  44,19,"Ur ssem$waôet iman nnwen, zdat Öebbi. Nek, usi$ d $uôwen, s udabu n ûûeê"
  44,20,"Nek, ad iyi Isseô Mass iw u d Mass nnwen, ur iyi tôeoomem"
  44,21,"Ma ur iyi tuminem ara, aâzlet iyi"
  44,22,Inuj $eô Mass is ar wigi d agdud ibe$wviyen
  44,23,"Awi imdanen iW deg iv. War ccekk, a kwen in vefôen"
  44,24,"Eoo ill ildi; nitni, ih, d lâaskeô ara i$emqen"
  44,25,"Ay ooan di tebêirin, akked tliwa"
  44,26,"igran, ixxamen ukyisen"
  44,27,l$it swayes zehhun
  44,28,Akka ay ten Nefka d lweôt i ugdud nniven
  44,29,"Ur d run, fellasen, igenni akked tmurt. Ur ggunin"
  44,30,"Ni$ Nsellek At Isôail, seg uâaqeb isdullun"
  44,31,"si Ferâun, i illan, s tidep, d amnefxi ger imaâfan"
  44,32,S tmusni ay ten Nefren deg imavalen
  44,33,"Nefka yasen seg issekniyen, wid ujeôôeb ipbegginen"
  44,34,"Ih, widak la qqaôen"
  44,35,"Siwa tameppant nne$ tamezwarut, ur fella$ tanekra"
  44,36,"Awit ed imezwura nne$, ma tessawalem tidep"
  44,37,"Menyif nitni ne$ agdud n Tubbaâ, akked wid i ten id izwaren? Nessenger iten. S tidep, nitni llan d ibe$wviyen"
  44,38,"Ur Nexliq ara tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, i wurar"
  44,39,"Nxelq iten kan s tidep, maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen"
  44,40,"S tidep, ass n ufraz, ad mlilen meôôa"
  44,41,"Ass ideg aêbib ur i$ennu aêbib, s wacemma; nitni ur pwasellken"
  44,42,"Kkes ed wid i$ef Iêun Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  44,43,"Ih, ttejôa n Zaqqum"
  44,44,uççi umednub
  44,45,"am nnêas ifsin, ippayzag di tâabbuvin"
  44,46,akken ppayzagen waman
  44,47,"Ddemt ep, zu$ôet ep, ar pnaûfa ujajiê"
  44,48,"sinna, smiret sufella uqeôôu s, aâaqeb ippayzagen"
  44,49,"Jeôôeb! Ni$ keçç d uzmir, d ukyis"
  44,50,"Ih, wagi d ayen i la tepcukkum"
  44,51,"Wanag wid iêezzben, deg umekkan n laman"
  44,52,di leonanat akked tliwa
  44,53,"lebsa nnsen s leêrir, leêrir iêewwcen. Mqabalen"
  44,54,"Akka, a ten Njewweo akked têuôtin lâin"
  44,55,"A d ssutren, dinna, yal izwayen, di laman"
  44,56,"Ur pjeôôiben, dinna, tameppant, siwa tameppant tamezwarut. Isellek iten seg uâaqeb ujajiê"
  44,57,"D lfevl n Mass ik, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  44,58,"Nsehhel it kan, s tmeslayt ik, amendeô ma a d mmektin"
  44,59,"Ggani, ula d nitni la pganin"
  45,1,Ëm
  45,2,"Tarusi n Tezmamt s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  45,3,"Di tmurt akked igenwan, s tidep, llan issekniyen i lmumnin"
  45,4,"Di lxelq nnwen, akked wayen id Issefôuôex n lewêuc, d issekniyen i ugdud ipputebbten"
  45,5,"Di lemgarda n yiv akked wass, akked wayen id Issrusu Öebbi n ôôeéq, seg igenni - Issidir yis tamurt, deffir tmeppant is -, deg udewwel n wavu, issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen"
  45,6,"D wigi ay d issekniyen n Öebbi; Nemmal ak ten, s tidep. Anwa ameslay ara amnen, deffir Öebbi akked issekniyen iS"
  45,7,A ssxev n yal akeddab amednub
  45,8,"Issemêas i issekniyen n Öebbi, qqaôen as ten, sinna, iggernen di tem$weô, amzun ur asen isli. Ihi, becceô it s uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  45,9,"Ma illa wayen iwumi isla, seg issekniyen nne£, ad ittihi fellas. I widak, aâaqeb isdullun"
  45,10,"Deffir sen Loahennama. Ur ten i$ennu s wacemma wayen kesben akked wayen rran d imawlan, war Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb abarar"
  45,11,"Tagi d nnhaya. Wid iugin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, fellasen aâaqeb n daâwessu taqeôêant"
  45,12,"Öebbi i Inuben fellawen s yill; ipcali, fellas, lbabuô, s lameô iS; a pnadim l$it iS. Amar a ppesnemrem"
  45,13,"Inub fellawen s wayen akw illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt. Akw s$uôeS. S tidep, deg waya, d issekniyen i ugdud ismektayen"
  45,14,"Ini i wid iumnen ad semmêen i wid ur negguni ara ussan n Öebbi, iwakken ad Ikafi agdud $ef wayen keppben"
  45,15,"Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win ifalîan, mgal is. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen tu$alin nnwen"
  45,16,"Ni$ Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt, ûûwab, lambiyya. Nôeéq iten s wayen ilhan. Nesmenyaf iten i imavalen"
  45,17,"Nefka yasen abeggen si Lameô. Ur mgarraden, armi i ten id tusa tmusni, wa iqheô wa. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden"
  45,18,"Sinna, Nebbwi k deg ubrid n Lameô. Ddu degs, ur teddu akked chawi n wid ur nessin"
  45,19,"Ih, nitni ur ak d ppawin acemma s$uô Öebbi. Imednas, ih, d imawlan wa n wa. Öebbi d Bab n wid ipêezziben"
  45,20,"Ayagi d assekni i l$aci, d nnhaya u d aêunu i ugdud ipputebbten"
  45,21,"Ne$ $ilen wid imôôeôen iman nnsen s tucmitin, a ten Neêseb am wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d imuddiren ne$ d lmeggtin. Dir it uêuddu nnsen"
  45,22,"Öebbi Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep, iwakken yal amdan ad ippuqeîîi af wayen ikseb. Nitni ur pwadensen"
  45,23,"Twalav win irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi is? Itelf it Öebbi, asali $uôeS. Iskweô as ul, timejjin, Irra yas aâbôuq af allen is. Anwa ara t inhun, deffir Öebbi? Day u la tesmektayem ara"
  45,24,"Nnan: \"i illan kan, d tudert nne$, di ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir. Ad a$ in$en kan d akud\". £ef ayagi, ur sâin kra n tmusni. Nitni $ilen kan"
  45,25,"Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, anamer nnsen, siwa mara d inin: \"erret ed imezwura nne$, ma tessawalem tidep"
  45,26,"Ini: \"Öebbi Issidir ikwen, sinna, Ineqq ikwen. Sinna a kwen Issemlil ass n tnekra, ur illi degs ccekk\". Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  45,27,"N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir, ass nni, ad xesôen ucmiten"
  45,28,"A pwaliv yal lois $ef tgwecrar, yal lois ipwanced ar tezmamt is. Assa, a p$eltem ayen txeddmem"
  45,29,"Tagi d tazmamt nne£, tessawal tidep fellawen. Nella Nepjerrid ayen akw txeddmem"
  45,30,"Ihi, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem, Mass nnsen, s aêunu S. Wagi d rrbeê n ûûeê"
  45,31,"Wanag wid ijehlen: \"day ur awen $ôan ara issekniyen iW? Tesme$wôem iman nnwen, tellam d agdud ibe$wviyen"
  45,32,"Mi nnan: \"ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep; imir, ur degs ccekk\", tennam: \"ur neéôi d acu ay d imir; $uône$ d nnwaya kan, ur nepputebbet"
  45,33,"Ad asen d vehôent tucmitin xedmen, ad asen izzi wayen i$ef ttihin"
  45,34,"Ad asen Inin: \"assa, a kwen Neppu, akken teppum timlilit n wass nnwen agi. Axxam nnwen d times, ur awen illi useîîaô"
  45,35,"Ayagi, acku kunwi la tettihim $ef issekniyen n Öebbi. T$uôô ikwen tudert n ddunit. Assa, ur d teff$en segs\". Ur isti$fiô êedd fellasen"
  45,36,"I Öebbi annuz, Mass igenwan, Mass n tmurt, Mass imavalen"
  45,37,"I Neppa akw ayen iufraren, di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  46,1,Ëm
  46,2,"Tarusi n Tezmamt s$uô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  46,3,"Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep, ar lajel ipwassnen. Wid ijehlen numren ayen u$uô pwanedôen"
  46,4,"Ini: \"day ur twalam ara wigi u$uô la tepnujum, war Öebbi? Sseknet iyi d, d acu xelqen si tmurt, ne$ ma sâan amur deg igenwan? Awit iyi d tazmamt id izwaren tagi, ne$ lateô n tmusni, ma tessawalem tidep"
  46,5,"Anwa innetlafen sennig wid ipnujun, war Öebbi, $eô wayen ur asen d nepparra, ar ass n tnekra, u nitni stehzan deg unuju nnsen"
  46,6,"Mara twafesrem imdanen, ad ilin d icenga nnsen, ad skiddben aâbad nnsen"
  46,7,"Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, wid iugin tidep, mi ten id tusa, ad inin: \"wagi d ssêur n ûûeê"
  46,8,"Ne$ ad inin: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"lemmer it id snulfa$, ur tezmirem ad iyi tsellkem, s wacemma, si Öebbi. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, acu têekkum fellas. Iqadd Neppa d Anagi gari yidwen. Neppa, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  46,9,"Ini: \"ur lli$, ger imazanen, d win id isnulfuyen. Ur éôi$ acu ara ivôun yidi, ne$ yidwen. La îîafaôe$, kan, ayen iyi d ippuweêêan. Aql i, kan, nek, d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  46,10,"Ini: \"meyyzet ma, ayagi, s$uô Öebbi, u tnekôem t? Icehhed unagi n At Isôail, $ef lmetl is, d$a iumen. Tesme$wrem iman nnwen\". Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas"
  46,11,"Nnan wid ijehlen, i wid iumnen: \"lemmer d ayen ilhan, ur a$ zeggwiren $uôes\". Imi ur pwanhan ara syis, qqaôen: \"ayagi d tikerkas n zik"
  46,12,"Uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Tagi d Tazmamt itebbiten, s wawalen n taâôabt, a ppendeô wid idensen, a ppessefôeê lâuûam"
  46,13,"Ih, wid iqqaôen: \"Mass nne$ d Öebbi, d$a îfen degs, ur ppagaden, ur $weblen"
  46,14,"Widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen, d arraz n wayen xeddmen"
  46,15,"Nweûûa amdan ar lewqama s imawlan is. Imma s temêen s tadist, temêen di tinnufra. Ger tadist akked ujumi, caret wagguren. Armi ibbwev d anqaqôi, issawev kuéet isegwasen, inna: \"a Mass iw! Eoo iyi a K snemmre$ af l$it i $ T$atev, nek akked lwaldin iw; ad xedme$ ayen ilhan ara K iôavin. Efk iyi d tarwa ilhan. Aql i utube$ K, aql i seg imvuâen"
  46,16,"£uô wigi, Nqebbel lmefruz igiten nnsen, a Nessuref i tucmitin nnsen, ger at Loennet; d lemâahda n tidep, i sen ippuwaââden"
  46,17,"Win innan i imawlan is: \"tfuh nnwen! Day yi tâahdem a d kkre$? Ni$ âaddan isuta uqbel i\". Nitni teppren tacvaî n Öebbi: \"a ssexv ik, amen! Ih, lmâahda n Öebbi, d tidep\". A d yini: \"ayagi, siwa tiêkayin imezwura"
  46,18,"D wigi i$ef iûaô wawal iaânan leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i ten id izwaren. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen"
  46,19,"I akw tiseddarin n wayen xedmen, iwakken ad yili warraz igiten nnsen. Nitni ur pwadensen"
  46,20,"Ass ideg ara kecmen ar tmes, wid ijehlen: \"tvegâam tiéidanin i s tezham, di tmeddurt nnwen di ddunit. Assa, a ppeppuqeîîim s uâaqeb isdullun, imi tessem$waôem iman nnwen di tmurt, ur teklalem; imi tellam tbe$wlem"
  46,21,"Mmekti d agmat n Âad, mi indeô agdud is deg igidan, u, s tidep, âaddan d ineddaôen zdat es, u zdeffir es: \"siwa Öebbi ara tâabdem. Nek ugade$, fellawen, aâaqeb n wass abarar"
  46,22,"Nnan d: \"day a$ d tusiv, ad a$ tfaôqev akked iôebbiten nne$? Awi a$ d ayen i$ef la $ tessagwadev, ma tessawalev tidep"
  46,23,"Inna: \"tamusni ar Öebbi kan. Ssawve$ awen ayen i$ef id ppuceggâa$. Maca, wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin"
  46,24,"Mi t walan d asigna id ileêêun ar t$wezza nnsen, nnan: \"wagi d asigna ar a$ d iawin ageffur\". Xaîi! D ayen i$ef têarem, d avu, degs aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  46,25,"ad isqucc yal cci, s lameô n Mass is. Gwran d ur tepwaliv siwa ixxamen nnsen. Akka i Nepqeîîi igduden ibe$wviyen"
  46,26,"Ni$ Nessakrer asen ayen ur awen Nessakrer. Nefka yasen imeééu$en, allen, akked wulawen. Ula i sen d bbwin deg wacemma imeééu$en, allen, akked wulawen, mi skaddben issekniyen n Öebbi. Ayen i$ef ttihin, izzi d fellasen"
  46,27,"Ni$ nessenger akw timdinin i wen d izzin, u Nenewwel asent issekniyen, amar a d u$alent s abrid"
  46,28,"Acimi ur ten sellken ara wid rran d iôebbiten iééaéan, war Öebbi? Xaîi! Ooan ten. D ayagi ay d tikerkas nnsen, u d wayen id snulfuyen"
  46,29,"Mi k ed Nebbwi agraw n leonun, ad ssemêessen i Leqwôan; mi s êedôen, nnan: \"êesset\"! Mi ifukk, u$alen s agdud nnsen d ineddaôen"
  46,30,"Nnan: \"a yagdud nne$, aql a$ nesla i Tezmamt id irsen, deffir Musa, id itebbten ayen ip id izwaren, i inehhun ar tidep akked ubrid uwqim"
  46,31,"A yagdud nne$, erret awal i uberraê n Öebbi, amnet yiS, ad awen Isemmeê seg ibekkaven nnwen, a kwen Isellek seg uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  46,32,"Win isâaweégen i uberraê n Öebbi, ur ipsellik di tmurt, ur ippaf imawlan, war Neppa. Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  46,33,"Day ur walan ara ar Öebbi d Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, ur Ifcil seg uxlaq nnsen? Izmer a d Issider lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  46,34,"Ass ideg ara d rsen, ar tmes, wid ijehlen: \"maççi s tidep ayagi\"? A d inin: \"ih, s Mass nne$\"! A d Yini: \"jeôôbet aâaqeb $ef wayen la tnekôem"
  46,35,"Eûbeô akken ûebôen wid iôeûmen seg imazanen. I nitni, ur p$awal. Ass ideg ara walin acu i sen ippuwaââden, amzun ur kminen siwa saâa n wass. D aberreê: \"anwa ara ipwakksen, siwa agdud icemten"
  47,1,"Wid ijehlen, u ssefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, Itlef igiten nnsen"
  47,2,"Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, umnen s wayen id irsen ar Muêemmed, u neppa d tidep s$uô Mass nnsen; Issemsa yasen tucmitin nnsen, Iûeggem asen lêala nnsen"
  47,3,"Ayagi, acku wid ijehlen îîafaôen tikerkas; ma d wid iumnen, îîafaôen tidep n Mass nnsen. Akka id Ippak Öebbi imedyaten nnsen i imdanen"
  47,4,"Mara d temlilem akked wid ijehlen, ewwtet ar tmegrav ar ten t$elbem. Arzet pen nezzeh. Sinna, d aserreê ne$ d feddu, alamma isers îôad tiâekkwmin is. Akka, lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili I$leb iten, maca a kwen Ijeôôeb, kra s kra. Wid ipwan$an deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur pôuêun igiten nnsen, d awez$i"
  47,5,"A ten Inhu, ad Iûeggem lêala nnsen"
  47,6,A ten Issekcem di Loennet i sen Imla
  47,7,"A wid iumnen! Ma tefkam afus i Öebbi, ad awen Ifk afus, ad awen itebbet isurifen"
  47,8,"Wid ijehlen, ay amxix nnsen, ad weddôen igiten nnsen"
  47,9,"Ayagi, acku ugwin ayen id Issers Öebbi; ihi, Imêa igiten nnsen"
  47,10,"Aâni ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d imezwura nnsen? Issexv iten Öebbi. Am akka i ijehliyen"
  47,11,"Ayagi, acku Öebbi d bab n wid iumnen. Ijehliyen, ur asen illi bab"
  47,12,"Ih, Öebbi ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Wid ijehlen zehhun, teppen akken itepp lmal. D times ay d leqôaô nnsen"
  47,13,"Acêal n at temdinin i yifen, di tezmert, tamdint i k id iéâan! Nesqucc iten, ur asen illi useîîaô"
  47,14,"Day win illan ar ubeggen n Mass is, am win, iwumi ppucebbêen yir igiten is, u iîîafaôen chawi nnsen"
  47,15,"Amek tga Loennet i ippuwaââden i wid ipêezziben: degs isaffen n waman ur nxeppeô, isaffen n yi$i ur tfessed lbenna s, isaffen n ccôab aéidan i wid itessen, isaffen n tament ippuneqqan. Degs, i nitni, yal ppemôa, akked ssmaê n Mass nnsen. Day am wid iwekkôen di tmes; sswan ten s waman ippayzagen, ara icergen afwad nnsen"
  47,16,"Llan garasen wid i k issemêasen. Sifat ff$en d s$uôek, ad inin i wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni: \"d acu id inna kan, llinna\"? Wigi d wid iwumi Isle$ Öebbi ulawen, teddun kan d chawi nnsen"
  47,17,"Wid ipwanhan, Irna asen nnhaya, Ifka yasen aêezzeb nnsen"
  47,18,"Day la pôaoun kan imir, a ten id ias, deqzalla? Ni$ usant ed licaôat is. Ma iusa d $uôsen, iwumi t usmekti nnsen"
  47,19,"Cfu ar, s tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi; ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik, akked wid n lmumnin, argaz tameîîut. Öebbi Iéôa anda têebkem, akked wanda tberrkem"
  47,20,"La qqaôen wid iumnen: \"a lemmer a d ters tsuôep\"! Maca, mi d ters tsuôep tuêkimt, ideg id ipwader umennu$, a pwaliv at wul iblan, la k id pmuqulen s tiî n win tessexcawat tmeppant. Yif it i nitni"
  47,21,"wannuz, akked wawal uwqim. Mi ipwagzem ôôay, ma ssawlen tidep ar Öebbi yif it i nitni"
  47,22,"Day maççi, ma twexxôem, ahat a ppesfesdem tamurt, a pfaôqem alag nnwen"
  47,23,"Wigi d wid i Ixza Öebbi; Isgugem iten, Isder$el iéôi nnsen"
  47,24,"Day ur pmeyyizen ara Leqwôan, ne$ u$alent tsergal $ef wulawen"
  47,25,"Ih, wid ixedâan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ikellex iten Cciîan. Iooa ten tallit"
  47,26,"Ayagi, acku nitni nnan i wid iugin ayen d Issader Öebbi: \"ad awen na$ awal di kra n lumuô\". Öebbi Iéôa lesrar nnsen"
  47,27,"Amek ihi, ma ddment lmalayek leôwaê nnsen, la ten kkatent ar udmawen nnsen, iârar nnsen"
  47,28,"Akka, ihi, ddan akked wayen isserfayen Öebbi. Ugin llza S. D$a Isseôxes igiten nnsen"
  47,29,"Ne$ $ilen at wul amehzul, ard awez$i, ur d Issuffu$ ara Öebbi leb$wev nnsen"
  47,30,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad ak ten id Nessken, war ccekk, a ten tâaqlev ar udem nnsen, a ten tâaqlev ar ûûenf umeslay. Öebbi Issen igiten nnwen"
  47,31,"S tidep, a kwen Njeôôeb, alamma Nessen imjuhad, akked iûebôiyen, segwen. A Njeôôeb isallen nnwen"
  47,32,"Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, i inuqmen Amazan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ur vuôôen Öebbi s wacemma. Ad Isseôxes igiten nnsen"
  47,33,"A wid iumnen! A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan, ur ssiôxiset igiten nnwen"
  47,34,"Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, sinna, mmuten d ijehliyen, war ccekk, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i"
  47,35,"Ur ppiôhifet, ur ssuturet tifrat, mara tilim d ine$laben! U Öebbi yidwen, ur kwen Ipêewwio, d awez$i, seg igiten nnwen"
  47,36,"Tameddurt di ddunit, d urar kan, akked lhawiyya. Ma tumnem u têezbem, ad awen d Ifk arrazen nnwen. Ur awen issutur ayla nnwen"
  47,37,"Ma Issuter awen t, a kwen Icebbwel, a pcuêêem, a d iffe$ leb$wev nnwen"
  47,38,"D kunwi i ipwanecden a pseddqem deg ubrid n Öebbi. Llan degwen wid ipcuêêun. Win ipcuêêun, ipcuêêu kan $ef yiman is. Öebbi d Asâay, kunwi d igellilen. Ma twexxôem, a kwen Ineûûef s ugdud ur nelli segwen. D$a ur ppemcabin $uôwen"
  48,1,"Ih, Nefya yak l$elb iberrzen"
  48,2,"iwakken ad Isemmeê Öebbi ibekkaven ik id izwaren akked wid igwran. Ad ak Itim l$it iS, a k Iawi d ubrid uwqim"
  48,3,A k Iall Öebbi tallalt tuzmirt
  48,4,"D Neppa id Issersen talwit deg ulawen n lmumnin, iwakken ad yim$uô liman nnsen. N Öebbi Iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga Iééeô, d Bab n ûûwab"
  48,5,"Iwakken ad Issekcem wid akked tid iumnen, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Ad asen Issemsu tucmitin nnsen. D wagi, ar Öebbi, ay d rrbeê abarar"
  48,6,"Ad Iâaqeb ixabiten, tixabitin, imcurak, timcurak, wid id ipfekkiôen Öebbi yir afekkeô. Izzi yasen ddens. Irfa Öebbi fellasen, Ixza ten. Ihegga yasen d Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip"
  48,7,"N Öebbi iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  48,8,"Ih, Nuzen ik id d anagi, d abcir, d aneddaô"
  48,9,"iwakken a ppamnem s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a T kfum, ad aS tanzem, a T tesbuccuâem taûebêit, tameddit"
  48,10,"Wid iâaqden yidek âaqden kan d Öebbi. Afus n Öebbi nnig ufus nnsen. Win iêenten, d imanis kan i isseênet. Win iîîfen deg wayen i$ef iâuhed Öebbi, ad as Ifk arraz abarar"
  48,11,"Ad ak inin wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: \"i $ ice$wlen, d ayla nne$ akked twaculin nne$. Ssuter a neppusemmeê\". Qqaôen s yilsawen nnsen, ayen ur nelli deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: \"anwa ara kwen iselken si Öebbi, s wacemma, ma Ib$a yawen vveôô, ne$ ma Ib$a yawen aba$uô? Xaîi, Izga Öebbi Ippuxebbeô af wayen txeddmem"
  48,12,"Xaîi, t$ilem Amazan akked lmumnin ur d ppu$alen ara, d awez$i, ar twaculin nnsen. Ayagi, issefôeê ulawen nnwen. Nnwaya nnwen dir ip. Kunwi d agdud imsenger"
  48,13,"Wid ur numin s Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, ihi, aql a£ Nhegga d ajajiê i ijehliyen"
  48,14,"N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan, Ipâuqub win i S ihwan. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  48,15,"A d inin wid igwran: \"ma tôuêem a d t$eltem, ooet a$ a neddu yidwen\". B$an ad bedlen awalen n Öebbi. Ini: \"ur teppeddum yidne$, d awez$i. Akka ay d izwar wawal n Öebbi\". A d inin: \"teêsedm a$\"! Xaîi, cwiî kan ay fehhmen"
  48,16,"Ini i wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: \"a ppepwanecdem s agdud amaâwaôu, uqsiê; a t tenna$em, ne$ ad anzen. Ma tu$em awal, ad awen Ifk Öebbi arraz igerzen. Ma twexxôem, akken twexxôem uqbel, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê"
  48,17,"Ur telli tiyta deg uder$al, ne$ deg urejdal, ne$ deg umuvin. Win iunzen i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a t Issekcem di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Win iwexxôen, a t Iâaqeb s lqeôê"
  48,18,"Ni$ Iôuva Öebbi lmumnin, mi âaqden yidek, seddaw ttejôa. Iéôa i illan deg ulawen nnsen, Issers d fellasen talwit, I$na ten s l$elb aqôib"
  48,19,"akked waîas n lerbaê, ara îîfen. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  48,20,"Iwaââed awen Öebbi a d teîîfem lerbaê aîas. I$awel awen d deg waya. Ikkes fellawen afus n medden. Akken ad yili ussekni i lmumnin, a kwen iawi d ubrid uwqim"
  48,21,"Tayev, iwumi ur tezmirem, ihi, Izzi as Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Izmer i yal cci"
  48,22,"Lemmer i kwen nnu$en wid ijehlen, ad rewlen, sinna, ur ppafen bab, ne$ asettaô"
  48,23,"D tannumi n Öebbi i illan si zik. Ur teppafev abeddel, d awez$i, di tannumi n Öebbi"
  48,24,"D Neppa i Ikksen afus nnsen segwen, akked ufus nnwen segsen, di te$zut n Mekka, siwev Iss$elb ikwen fellasen. Öebbi Izga Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  48,25,"D nitni i ijehlen. Swexxôen kwen si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ugin ad iawev usfel s amkan is. Lemmer maççi d lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, ur ten tessinem, a ten têazem ur teéôim; segsen a d tegwrim di le$ôuô - ni$ Öebbi Issekcam s aêunu S, win i S ihwan - lemmer mfaôaqen, yili, war ccekk, Nesâadda, $ef wid segsen ijehlen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  48,26,"Mi rran wid ijehlen, aêernun deg ulawen nnsen, aêernun n war tussna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS af Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Iqqen asen awal uêezzeb. Iwata ten, klalen t. Öebbi Izga Iéôa yal cci"
  48,27,"Ni$ Issawev Öebbi, i Umazan iS, tamu$li s tidep: war ccekk, a pkecmem Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ma Irad Öebbi, di laman, iqweôôa nnwen ûûeîlen u qeôcen, ur teppagwadem. Iéôa ayen ur teéôim. Ihegga yawen d, ugwar aya, l$elb aqôib"
  48,28,"Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS s nnhaya, akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifrer $ef ddin meôôa. Iqadd Öebbi d Anagi"
  48,29,"Muêemmed d Amazan n Öebbi. Wid illan yides, qesêen ar ijehliyen, êninit garasen. A ten twaliv îîinizen, kennun, ssuturen lfevl s$uô Öebbi akked llza. Ccama nnsen, deg udmawen nnsen, d lateô n lekni. Ata wayen i ten icban di Tuôa akked wayen i ten icban di Linoil: am uâaqqa, iger ed im$i s, isoehd it. Ad iuzur, ad iâaooeô $ef yile$ is. Ippaâoab ifellaêen; i$webben yissen ijehliyen. Iwaââed Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz abarar, i wid degsen iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  49,1,"A wid iumnen! Ur zeggwiret zdat Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  49,2,"A wid iumnen! Ur zzuhriyet tu$ac nnwen, sennig ta$wect n Nnbi. Ur zaââvet $uôes, akken tepzaââvam garawen, mulac ad mêun igiten nnwen, kunwi ur tfaqem"
  49,3,"Ih, wid issrusun ûut n ta$wect nnsen, ar Umazan n Öebbi, d wid iwumi Issefsi Öebbi ulawen nnsen, ar uêezzeb. Ad asen ippunefk ssmaê akked warraz abarar"
  49,4,"Ih, tegwti n wid ik n issawlen, deffir texxamin, ur pmeyyizen"
  49,5,"Lemmer ûbiôen ard teff$ev $uôsen, ppif i nitni. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  49,6,"A wid iumnen! Aballa$ ma ibbwi yawen d asali, ppuêeqqeqet, mulac a pvuôôem agdud, war tamusni, a ppu$alem tnedmem deg wayen txedmem"
  49,7,"Cfut illa garawen Umazan n Öebbi. Ma issemêes awen deg waîas n lumuô, a pjafem. Maca, Öebbi Issaâzez awen liman, Imelleê it deg ulawen nnwen, Isseôéeg awen tijehli, dd$el, lmaâûegga. Widak d wid ipwanhan"
  49,8,"D lfevl s$uô Öebbi, d l$it. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab"
  49,9,"Ma nnu$ent snat n îayfat n lmumnin, êuddet pent. Ma tebw$ev yiwet degsent, $ef tayev, nna$et tin ibwe$ven alamma tevfeô lameô n Öebbi. Ma tevfeô it, ssemûalêet pent, s lmizan. Wezznet. Öebbi Iêemmel wid iwezznen"
  49,10,"Lmumnin d atmaten kan i illan. Ssemûalêet atmaten nnwen, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar fellawen aêunu"
  49,11,"A wid iumnen! £uôwat ad imaâlek ugdud $ef wayev, ahat d widen i ten yifen. Ne$ tilawin $ef tiyav, ahat d tiden i tent yifen. Ur pqeôôidet iman nnwen, ur pmirgamet s tselleqwbin. Dir it isem n dd$el, anda illa liman. Wid ur nutub ara, d widak ay d imednas"
  49,12,"A wid iumnen! Janbet aîas n nnwaya. Ih, nnwaya, tikwal, d abekkav. Ur ppemâassat ara. Ur kkatet wa deg wa. Day ib$u yiwen, degwen, ad içç aksum n gmas lmegget? A t tagwim. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  49,13,"A yimdanen! Ni$ Nxelq ikwen si ddker akked nnta. Nerra kwen d igduden, d laâôac, a ppemyussanem. Ihi, ukyis nnwen amxallef, ar Öebbi, d win degwen ipêezziben sennig wiyav. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa, Ippuxebbeô"
  49,14,"Nnan uâôaben n ucluê: \"numen\". Ini: \"ur tuminem\". Maca init ed: \"nunez\"; ur ikcim ara liman ar wulawen nnwen. Ma tôuvam Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur awen Isôuêu acemma seg igiten nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  49,15,"Lmumnin d wid kan iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, d$a, ur pcukun. Pna$en s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. D widak ay d imawlan n tidep"
  49,16,"Ini: \"day ad aS temlem i Öebbi, ddin nnwen\"? Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Issen yal cci"
  49,17,"Rran ak annuz nnsen, d tajmilt. Ini: \"ur iyi telli tejmilt deg annuz nnwen. Xaîi, d Öebbi ikwen I$aten mi kwen Inha ar liman, ma d imawlan n tidep ay tellam"
  49,18,"Ih, Öebbi Issen tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"